NK039(ti)004:1: // dpal ldan lha mo'i mchod phrin chen mo don kun grub pa'i dbyangs snyan bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)004:3: bla ma mchog dang yum chen pha rol phyin //
NK039(ti)004:4: bstan dgra bsgral slad khros pa'i skur bstan pa //
NK039(ti)004:5: ma cig 'dod khams dbang mo la btud nas //
NK039(ti)004:6: gang de mchod cing bsgrub pa'i cho ga dbye /
NK039(ti)004:7: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ma mo
NK039(ti)004:8: mkha' 'gro thams cad kyi spyi rje bdud mo srog
NK039(ti)004:9: gi gzer chung ma'am dpal ldan lha mo nag mo
NK039(ti)004:10: rang byung rgyal mo 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug
NK039(ti)004:11: ma zhes gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i srung ma
NK039(ti)004:12: chen mo gang de'i mchod cing bsgrub pa'i tshul la
NK039(ti)004:13: don gsum / sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:15: rjes kyi bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:16: dang po sngon du bya ba'i rim pa la /
NK039(ti)004:20: kha byang shar du blta ba'i brag phug gam /
NK039(ti)004:21: lha 'dre drag po gnas pa'i sar /
NK039(ti)004:22: bye brag la spyi mthun dam ldan 'du ba'i dben
NK039(ti)004:23: gnas su bsgrub par bya ste rnal 'byor pa mdo
NK039(ti)004:24: sgyu yang phur gang rung gi dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK039(ti)004:26: bye brag ma mo'i srog gtad dam /
NK039(ti)004:29: rgyud sde nas 'byung ba'i bsnyen chen dang /
NK039(ti)004:32: gnyen po lha yi bsnyen pa thon pa'i rnal 'byor
NK039(ti)004:33: pas ras bris kyi cho ga ltar bris pa'i sku
NK039(ti)004:34: thang dgram pa'i mdun dkyil 'khor mda' gang gru bzhi
NK039(ti)004:35: pa'i steng du / rten rdzas kyi rim pa ni /
NK039(ti)004:36: rten gyi gtor ma 'bru sna tshogs las byas pa'i
NK039(ti)004:37: phye la rak+ta chang phud bdud rtsi'i sbrus pa'i dpal
NK039(ti)004:38: bshos snying gzugs ma thod mkhar bcas pa phyag len
NK039(ti)004:42: khrims 'chal sha la sogs pa'i sha sna tshogs kyi bskor /
NK039(ti)004:43: mda' bya rgod ma bzang po gcig la skyes dar
NK039(ti)004:44: ma grir shi ba'i tsit+ta'i rtsa sbubs dbus mar 'bod
NK039(ti)004:45: rbad bsad gsum gyi sngags gri khrag dang mtshal gyis
NK039(ti)004:46: bris la gzhug / dar nag gis bril la mad'i mgul du btag go //
NK039(ti)004:47: gzhan yang tsakli dang ne'u le'i rkyal bu'i nang du mi dbang gi dbang po lnga dang /
NK039(ti)004:48: bye ru la sogs rin po che sna tshogs dang /
NK039(ti)004:56: mi bsad pa'i lcags las brdung ba'i ral gri sor brgyad pa yu bar b+h+yohbrisa pa gcig dang /
NK039(ti)004:57: de rnams mda' yi mgul du btags la brten gtor steng gzugs /
NK039(ti)004:58: bla rdo dang srog 'khor yod na bshams /
NK039(ti)004:59: de'i steng dar nag gi gdug phub /
NK039(ti)004:60: rgyun du rten gtor rtsam gyis mthus /
NK039(ti)004:61: mtha' bskor du g.yas g.yon sman raka /
NK039(ti)004:63: gtor ma la mthun rdzas sbyar ba /
NK039(ti)004:66: 'dod yon sogs mchod pas bag dro zhing brjid chags par bskor la /
NK039(ti)004:71: sha dum ba lim rnams tshogs par byas la /
NK039(ti)004:76: sman khyad par gyi g.yab dar nag po b+h+yohyiga gi mtshan pa /
NK039(ti)004:77: mda' bya rgod ma'i mgul du bud med chur shi ba'i srin lag dang /
NK039(ti)004:78: ba dan rtse gsum rnams btags pa bkod /
NK039(ti)004:79: sgrub grogs rnams kyi mdun mi rkang gi dung dang rnga rol sogs 'du byas te /
NK039(ti)004:80: lte phur mnan pa sogs bsnyen sgrub dang 'brel na bya /
NK039(ti)004:81: sgrub rkyang ngam dus gtor tsam la mi dgos /
NK039(ti)004:82: bdag gi rnal 'byor bzlas pa dang bcas pa rdzogs nas /
NK039(ti)004:83: 'od gsal du bsdu ldang bya ba rnams ni thog mar bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:84: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnas yo byin brlabs pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:85: mchod cing bsgrub pa'i yul gsal gdab pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:86: de la gsol mchod ji ltar bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:88: h'u big+nana ta krit+ta h'u phata /
NK039(ti)004:89: ram yam kham gis bsangs sbyangs /
NK039(ti)004:91: stong pa'i ngang las sa phyogs dur khrod rol pa'i
NK039(ti)004:92: gzhal med chen po 'jigs su rung ba'i +aa yig
NK039(ti)004:93: las byung ba'i snod nor bu chu shel dang /
NK039(ti)004:95: bde skyong gi dung chen la sogs par yig las byung ba'i mchod rdzas ngo bo stong nyid la /
NK039(ti)004:97: byed las bde stong gi ye shes bskyed par byed pa /
NK039(ti)004:104: rol mo rnams zhi ba yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:114: bkra shis rdzas rtags sna bdun /
NK039(ti)004:115: ma d+aa na dang ru d+hir yi tshogs gtor /
NK039(ti)004:116: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga yi sman chen rigs lnga mnyam par sbyor ba'i rtsi dang 'dres pa /
NK039(ti)004:117: khams gsum zhen chags thams cad gcig tu bsdus pa'i dmar gyi rgya mtsho sbu phreng 'khrigs pa /
NK039(ti)004:118: gzugs sgra dri ro reg chos rdo rje'i lha mos
NK039(ti)004:119: sa dang bar snang gi khyon yongs su gang ba
NK039(ti)004:120: / h'u yig gi 'od kyis gnyis 'dzin dag pa'i
NK039(ti)004:121: ye shes las cir yang 'char bas re re'ang grangs
NK039(ti)004:122: med par 'phro ba'i 'dod 'byung gi dpal du 'char
NK039(ti)004:124: sngags drug phyag drug bya ste dri ma sbyang ba'i
NK039(ti)004:125: phyag rgya thal mo khang stong snying khar sbyar la
NK039(ti)004:127: mang por spel ba'i phyag rgya thal mo khang stong tshig zur can smin mtshams su sbyar la /
NK039(ti)004:128: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo sogs /
NK039(ti)004:129: ci 'dod bsgyur ba'i phyag rgya thal mo gong ma
NK039(ti)004:130: sbyar zhing 'og ma cung zad bskyed pa la kha
NK039(ti)004:133: so sor thob pa'i phyag rgya lag g.yon thal mo
NK039(ti)004:134: mchod sbyin snod btegs pa'i tshul du pus mor bzhag
NK039(ti)004:135: g.yas rdo rje khu tshur snying khar bzhag ste /
NK039(ti)004:136: dz+ny+aa na a wa lo ki sogs dgyes shing tshim
NK039(ti)004:137: par dbang ba'i phyag rgya lag g.yas mdzub mo gtor
NK039(ti)004:139: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta sogs mnyes nas don
NK039(ti)004:140: byed pa'i phyag rgya lag gnyis so sor bsnol mthe
NK039(ti)004:141: bong gshib la / na ma sa man ta bud+d+ha sogs /
NK039(ti)004:143: badz+ra ar+g+ham +aahmh'u nas shap+da +aahmh'u bar dang /
NK039(ti)004:146: sarba bid p+au ra dang sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa /
NK039(ti)004:149: d+harma ra ni tas mchod pa'i rol mos byin dbab bo //
NK039(ti)004:150: gnyis pa la gzhi rten gzhal yas khang gdan bcas gsal gdab pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:151: brten pa lha gsal gdab pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:152: de la ye shes pa bkug cing spyan 'dren bzhugs gsol bya ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:154: dang po la sems bskyed pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:157: sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK039(ti)004:158: de yi phyir sa lam gyi bar chad zhi zhing
NK039(ti)004:159: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung ba'i ched du dpal
NK039(ti)004:160: ldan lha mo chen mo bsgrub par bya'o //
NK039(ti)004:161: sems can bde dang sdug bsngal bde dang chos kun
NK039(ti)004:162: de ltar gsal ba'i kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems
NK039(ti)004:163: de'i rang bzhin gdod nas mi dmigs pa don dam
NK039(ti)004:164: byang chub kyi sems stod pa nyid do //
NK039(ti)004:165: s+w+aa b+ha wa sogs gnyis pa ni /
NK039(ti)004:166: stong pa'i ngang las skad cig mdun du yam ljang gu /
NK039(ti)004:168: b+h+r+aum yig smug nag 'bar ba rnams 'od du zhu ba las /
NK039(ti)004:169: 'thor byed drag tu 'khrugs pa'i rlung gi dkyil 'khor gru bzhi yangs shing rgya che /
NK039(ti)004:170: nang stong pa 'phang mtho'i zur la g.yo ba'i ba dan gyis mtshan pa'i steng du /
NK039(ti)004:171: dmar nag 'bar ba'i me dkyil rlung dang mtshungs pa
NK039(ti)004:172: shin tu gtum zhing rab tu mched pa'i steng na
NK039(ti)004:173: thod pa skom rlon rnying gsum gyis brtsigs pa la
NK039(ti)004:174: gnam lcags kyi gzer btab pa'i gzhal yas khang chen
NK039(ti)004:175: po gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK039(ti)004:176: 'dod snam mched pa'i sprin gyis gang ba'i drag po'i
NK039(ti)004:177: rta babs bzhi bzhi sogs pa'i mda' yab dang bcas
NK039(ti)004:178: pa / chu srin rgyal po'i sgo rgyan /
NK039(ti)004:179: bdud kyi mgo bo tshal par bkas pa'i ka gdan /
NK039(ti)004:187: bgegs kyi glo phreng 'byung po'i rkang lag gi shar bu byas pa'i steng /
NK039(ti)004:188: rin po che dbang gi rgyal po'i tog gis mdzes pa'i zhing chen gyi rgyal mtshan btsugs pa /
NK039(ti)004:189: dbus su zhing gi gdugs 'khor ba yangs shing rgya che ba blos rdzogs tshad gcig bskyed gsung /
NK039(ti)004:190: dbus gru gsum mthing nag ngos zla gam log gsum khrag mtsho 'khyil ba /
NK039(ti)004:191: de rgyab thod pa'i rwa ba de rgyab gru chad
NK039(ti)004:192: khyams dang bcas pa'i dbus gar+b+ha pa h'u zhes brjod
NK039(ti)004:193: pas 'og gi sa gzhi kun mi ro dang rta
NK039(ti)004:194: ro gcal du bkram pa mi khrag dang rta khrag
NK039(ti)004:195: gi mtsho 'khyil ba 'khor kun la zhing tshal pa'i
NK039(ti)004:196: gdan dang / dbus kyi gtso mo'i gnas su rang
NK039(ti)004:197: nyid yi dam gyi lte ba nas yi ge tihnaga
NK039(ti)004:198: gdan dang / po gcig spros / 'od du zhu
NK039(ti)004:199: ba las srin gyis sprulapa'i bong du dmar ga rlung
NK039(ti)004:200: gi gshogs pa can dbo dkar ba la zhing gi
NK039(ti)004:201: stan dang thod skom 'bar bas mtshan pa'i sga bstad
NK039(ti)004:202: gdan dang / po gcig spros / pa / srin po'i ya thod las snga ru byas shing /
NK039(ti)004:203: srin mo'i man 'gal las phyi ru dang /
NK039(ti)004:204: zhing gi lpags pas sga g.yogs byas pa /
NK039(ti)004:205: sbrul nag gis gong thag dang glo nan zhing chung
NK039(ti)004:206: ngu gnyis kyi smed byil lag pa gnyis 'phyang zhing
NK039(ti)004:207: skra mdud yar btags pa'i smed thung /
NK039(ti)004:209: b+aa su ta yi zhags pas mthur srab bcings pa /
NK039(ti)004:210: rus sbal nag po'i phog gu btab cing /
NK039(ti)004:211: mi mgo'i thod sdom bgyis pa'i snga shad g.yas na bdud kyi khram bam bkal cing /
NK039(ti)004:212: snga shad g.yon na mtshon gyi gru gu bcings pa /
NK039(ti)004:213: phyi shad g.yas na byang dmar bam po 'dogs shing /
NK039(ti)004:214: phyi shad g.yon na nad kyis rkyal pa 'gel ba /
NK039(ti)004:215: bong bu'i mjug ma'i rtsa ba g.yas gnyis na mig
NK039(ti)004:216: gnyis yod cing rna ba dkrog bzhin rlung dmar 'tshubs
NK039(ti)004:217: ma'i nang du rgyug pa dang bcas pa'i gzhal med
NK039(ti)004:218: khang gi phyi ye shes bskal pa'i me ri 'bar
NK039(ti)004:219: ba'i gur khang de'i phyir bskal pa'i rlung nag 'tshubs
NK039(ti)004:220: ma'i gur khang 'khor ba'i phyir na mu le mthing
NK039(ti)004:221: gi rgya mtsho rba rlabs kyi ri len par nus
NK039(ti)004:222: shing / 'od zer lnga yi mdangs phro ba /
NK039(ti)004:223: zhing bcu tshangs pa'i dgra ro dum bu nyil nyil
NK039(ti)004:224: g.yo zhing rgya khyon shin tu che ba'i mtha' mu
NK039(ti)004:226: dur khrod chen po'i sa gzhi 'jigs rung bkod pa'i
NK039(ti)004:227: tshogs ma tshang ba med pas gang ba na ma
NK039(ti)004:231: sman mo 'bum sde sogs ci dga' bar rtsen zhing /
NK039(ti)004:233: kang+ka nag po sogs bya tshogs lding zhing /
NK039(ti)004:234: lce spyang 'dur ba srin mos skan sgra gtogs shing /
NK039(ti)004:235: las byed mkha' 'gros bshugs glu len pa'i mthar ri
NK039(ti)004:236: bo brag dmar gnam la zug pa dang bcas pa
NK039(ti)004:237: gsal bar gyur / gnyis pa la gtso mo dang /
NK039(ti)004:240: de nas rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka nas yi ge m+aahnaga mo gcig 'phros /
NK039(ti)004:241: bong bu'i sga gong zhing chen bsnol ba'i gdan gyi steng /
NK039(ti)004:242: ram las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i thog tu dbab /
NK039(ti)004:243: de 'od du zhu ba las ral gri'i yu ba
NK039(ti)004:244: mar bstan pa rtse mo yar bstan pa gzhung ba
NK039(ti)004:245: rang la bstan pa'i so yu'i mtshams nas nyi ma'i
NK039(ti)004:246: thog tu mahnaga mo dang b+h+yohmathinga kas mtshan pa de
NK039(ti)004:249: sems can gyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK039(ti)004:250: 'jig rten gyi mkha' 'gro ma thams cad la phog /
NK039(ti)004:251: thams cad lha mo nag mo nyid du gyur /
NK039(ti)004:252: kun tshur 'dus ral gri la thim de las ral gri'i 'od zer spros /
NK039(ti)004:253: rgyal ba'i bstan pa la sdang ba'i dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad /
NK039(ti)004:254: tshur 'dus te ral gri 'od du zhu sngags kyi sgra rang sgrar grags pa ni /
NK039(ti)004:255: ro ru ro ru tri yod pa snang mod ma
NK039(ti)004:256: dag pa 'dra ste yi ge bco lnga par grags
NK039(ti)004:257: pa'i phyir / tsa pa la a shug+me h'u b+h+yo
NK039(ti)004:258: dza dzah skad cig gis sprul pa'i lha mo nag
NK039(ti)004:260: de yang dpal ye shes kyi lha mo nag mo
NK039(ti)004:261: chen mo sku mdog mthing nag la rngams pa zhal
NK039(ti)004:262: gcig phyag gnyis dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum me
NK039(ti)004:263: stag gi tsha tsha 'khrugs pas bdud bgegs log 'dren
NK039(ti)004:264: thams cad bsregs pa dam nyams dgra ro dum bur
NK039(ti)004:265: 'dral ba'i zhal gdangs shing mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa'i
NK039(ti)004:266: ljags 'dril ba / phyag g.yas sdig pa can gyi
NK039(ti)004:267: ral gri ye shes me ri 'tshubs pa nam mkha'
NK039(ti)004:268: ljags 'dril ba / la phyar ba / ral gri'i sting pa la dmar thig gcig snang gsungs /
NK039(ti)004:269: g.yon pas log lta can gyi khrag gis bkang ba'i b+han+ha lcang lo can thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK039(ti)004:270: sta zur g.yon gyi mchan na rin po ches phyur bur bkang ba'i ne'u le'u rkyal pa /
NK039(ti)004:271: kha nas rin po che phyur ba bsnams pa bong bu la phyir log tu bcib shing /
NK039(ti)004:272: mi yi thod pa'i yob chen la bardzisa pa /
NK039(ti)004:273: dbu skra khams nag gi ral pa gyen du thor tshugs su mtho zhing /
NK039(ti)004:274: thur du yang sa la bshar ba /
NK039(ti)004:275: dga' ba bcu drug gis thugs rgyud myos pa'i brdar rtsa chings /
NK039(ti)004:276: ral pa'i mtshams tshur thod pa skom po bcu drug gi phreng ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:277: thod skom rin po che'i rtse bran can lnga yis dbu brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)004:278: skabs 'dir bla ma kahthoga pa'i bzhed pa la thod
NK039(ti)004:279: skom bcu drug gi dbu 'khor mar brgyan pa las
NK039(ti)004:280: ma gsungs kyang / rgyud don man ngag gi lugs su byas /
NK039(ti)004:281: spyi bo'i gtsug na tshes brgyad pa'i zla ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:282: rma bya'i mdangs kyi rgyal mtshan brgyan cing /
NK039(ti)004:283: snyan g.yas pa'i steng na gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs
NK039(ti)004:284: brgyad pa seng ge dkar mo g.yu yi ral pa
NK039(ti)004:285: can gyis mdzes pa'i snyan cha dang /
NK039(ti)004:286: g.yon pa'i snyan cha gdengs ka can gyis sprul nag gis btags pa'i gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK039(ti)004:287: sku stod zhing chen lpags pa'i na bza' gsol zhing /
NK039(ti)004:288: sku smad snam bu g.yas phyogs smyugs ma'i mi skra'i re lde zhes kyang gsungs /
NK039(ti)004:290: g.yon phyogs glang po che'i ko barla rtsa bskor ba thung thung yin gsungs /
NK039(ti)004:292: stag lpags kyi sham thabs la sbrul nag gis sku rags bcings pa /
NK039(ti)004:293: mgo bo rlon pa lnga bcu'i do shal se ral khar thogs pa las khrag 'bab pa /
NK039(ti)004:294: 'khor lo'i skra kheb phyag zhabs dpung pa'i gdub bu /
NK039(ti)004:295: mchod phyir thog bcas rus pa'i phyag rgya lnga dang /
NK039(ti)004:296: yid bzhin nor bu'i mgul rgyan khrag zhag thal ba
NK039(ti)004:297: zhag gis mtshan mas btabs shing til mar gyis lus
NK039(ti)004:298: kun khyab par byugs pa zhabs la lcags sgrog gis
NK039(ti)004:299: mdzes shing / sku dang yan lag thams cad sbrul
NK039(ti)004:300: rigs lngas bcings pa'i lus las g.yu yi dril bus
NK039(ti)004:301: mdzes shing / bsil ba / lte bar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor tsha zhing bsregs pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:302: mtshon cha'i rdzong nas lha yi dmag dpung sprin gtib
NK039(ti)004:303: pa bzhin spro ba khro gtum bzod par dka' ba'i
NK039(ti)004:306: ma mo'i thugs ka nas 'khor gyi gnas so sor
NK039(ti)004:307: b+h+yo yig re spros pa 'od du zhu ba'i bong
NK039(ti)004:308: bu'i kha dur zhabs su khol mo re ma ti
NK039(ti)004:309: ste lha mo skems ma chu srin gyi mgo can
NK039(ti)004:310: sku mdog dmar nag zhal gcig gtso mo la phyogs
NK039(ti)004:311: la / g.yas pas rgyu zhags kyis bong bu khrid cing /
NK039(ti)004:312: g.yon pas sbrul nag gi zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)004:313: zhing lpags kyi sham thabs dang /
NK039(ti)004:314: sbrul nag gi se ral thog nas rgyug ste 'gro ba'i nyams can /
NK039(ti)004:315: gru gsum zla gam ngos kyi gtso mo'i mdun na gsum dang /
NK039(ti)004:316: g.yas g.yon du gnyis te bcas pa'i ma mo bdun ni /
NK039(ti)004:317: rdo rje kun grags ma dang kun tu bzang mo /
NK039(ti)004:318: rdo rje kun gsal mo dang /
NK039(ti)004:320: rdo rje 'od chags ma dang rdo rje gsal 'phro ma /
NK039(ti)004:321: rdo rje g.yu yi sgron mar bcas pa'i sku mdog
NK039(ti)004:322: nag mo gri khug dag thod pa khrag gis bkang
NK039(ti)004:323: ba 'dzin cing / gtso mo la mdun phyogs pas zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum gyis rol pa /
NK039(ti)004:324: gru gsum gyi zur gsum du ma mo gsum ni sku yi sprul pa re ma dza /
NK039(ti)004:325: gsung gi sprul pa re ma dzi /
NK039(ti)004:326: thugs kyi sprul pa re ma dzu rnams sku mdog
NK039(ti)004:327: nag mo g.yas lcags kyu g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa
NK039(ti)004:328: / de'i phyi rol du gru chad nang ma'i shar stod du dkar mo pho nya mdzes ma /
NK039(ti)004:329: lho stod sngon mo ral pa 'dzing ma /
NK039(ti)004:330: nub stod dmar mo dbang chen gtum mo //
NK039(ti)004:331: byang stod ser mo mkha' la bzhad ma bzhi g.yas ba dan /
NK039(ti)004:333: gru chad kyi shar smad seng ge dkar mo /
NK039(ti)004:336: byang du spyang gdong can ljang gu rnams kyang phyag na ba dan dang thod khrag thogs pa /
NK039(ti)004:337: de yi phyi khrag khyams la shar stod nas rim bzhin /
NK039(ti)004:344: lho stod nas rdo rje dmar mo /
NK039(ti)004:364: sgo bzhi rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu can /
NK039(ti)004:367: gsus 'dzin dril bu ma rnams sku mdog smug nag g.yas rdo rje dang /
NK039(ti)004:368: g.yon thod pa khrag gis bkang ba 'dzin pa /
NK039(ti)004:369: yang na sgyu 'phrul ltar bya bar gsungs /
NK039(ti)004:370: zhing gi gdan la brkyang bskum gyis rol pa /
NK039(ti)004:371: de ltar gsal ba'i ma mo thams cad kyang khro gtum sdang mig yon por blta bas /
NK039(ti)004:373: thod rlon dang snying gi phreng ba mgul du rgyang ba /
NK039(ti)004:374: mi yi rgyu ma rlon pa zhags su 'khyil ba nar mar 'dren cing /
NK039(ti)004:375: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs sbrul gyis 'ching ba /
NK039(ti)004:376: zhing lpags sked la dkris shing /
NK039(ti)004:377: mche ba khrag gis sbags pa'i rtse mo gnam lcags
NK039(ti)004:378: thog gi mda' ltar bgegs kyi glo ba'i ngos na
NK039(ti)004:380: thams cad kyang gtso mo'i bka' la nyan cing dam
NK039(ti)004:381: ldan rnal 'byor pas ci bsgo ba'i las yid bzhin
NK039(ti)004:382: du bsgrub pa / de yi phyi na dur khrod
NK039(ti)004:383: kyi 'khor sar b+h+yo yig las skyes pa 'khor ma
NK039(ti)004:384: du bsgrub pa / mo stong dang / bdud mo
NK039(ti)004:385: bye ba 'bum gyi tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad
NK039(ti)004:387: spyan nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor ltar 'bar zhing /
NK039(ti)004:388: 'od kyi mdog khrag ltar dmar ba /
NK039(ti)004:389: dar nag gi go zu 'ja' tshon gyi mtha' skud can gsol ba /
NK039(ti)004:391: sku mdog nag mo ral pa sngo dmar mthur du 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)004:392: g.yas pa rnams kyi gri gug dang /
NK039(ti)004:393: g.yon pa rnams na thod khrag thogs shing /
NK039(ti)004:394: mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa sngo dmar 'chang ba /
NK039(ti)004:395: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la mnab pa /
NK039(ti)004:396: 'jigs 'jigs rngam rngams su rol pa 'khor de dag
NK039(ti)004:397: thams cad kyang phrin las rnam bzhi'i rol pa bsam
NK039(ti)004:398: gyis mi khyab pa 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i sprin chen
NK039(ti)004:401: de ltar gsal ba'i gtso 'khor thams cad kyi spyi bor zla ba'i steng du dkar po /
NK039(ti)004:402: mgrin par pad ma'i steng du +aahdamara po /
NK039(ti)004:403: snying khar nyi ma'i steng du h'u sngon po rnams
NK039(ti)004:404: rgyal ba thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum gyi ngo
NK039(ti)004:407: bdag nyid lha'i thugs ka nas lcags kyu lta bu'i tsha zhing rtsub pa'i 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK039(ti)004:408: dag pa mkha' spyod kyi gzhal med /
NK039(ti)004:409: byang shar mtsho mu le mthing gi gur khang /
NK039(ti)004:410: ri rab ri yi rtse mo sum cu rtsa gsum
NK039(ti)004:411: gyi dpag bsam shing ljon pa rgyas pa'i lo ma'i
NK039(ti)004:412: tshal nub phyogs u rgyan byang chub shing gi drung
NK039(ti)004:413: la sogs rang bzhin dang khyad par gyi gnas mchog
NK039(ti)004:414: thams cad nas sngon gyi thugs dam rjes su bskul
NK039(ti)004:415: te dpal ldan lha mo nag mo chen po la
NK039(ti)004:416: / 'khor ye shes las dang 'jig rten gyi mkha'
NK039(ti)004:417: 'gro bye ba 'bum sde snang srid ma mo'i tshogs
NK039(ti)004:419: gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa skad cig gis byon par bsam la /
NK039(ti)004:420: dang po rdo rje ka go na'i rgya bcas /
NK039(ti)004:421: ru ru ro ru tsa pa la a shug+me h'u
NK039(ti)004:422: b+h+yo dza dzah e h+ye hi ma mo nag mo
NK039(ti)004:423: ting lam ma mo nag mo dun+tim b+h+yo dzah h+aum
NK039(ti)004:424: bam hohnaga mo dun b+h+yohkhyada par gyi g.yab dar /
NK039(ti)004:428: spyan 'dren che ba snyan pa'i dbyangs tshig dang bcas te /
NK039(ti)004:430: don dam dag pa chos dbyings dang nyid las //
NK039(ti)004:431: rgyal ba kun yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma //
NK039(ti)004:432: dpal ldan mkha' 'gro ma mo yongs kyi rje //
NK039(ti)004:433: mkha' 'gro'i 'khor lo che la 'dir gshegs shig /
NK039(ti)004:434: kun tu bzang mo dpal ldan thugs sprul ma //
NK039(ti)004:435: don dam dbyings na bskyed par mi mnga' yang //
NK039(ti)004:436: thugs rjes thabs kyi sems can gdul ba'i slad //
NK039(ti)004:437: ma 'gags stong pa che las bzhengs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:438: ma cig he ru ka dpal d+aak+ki mo //
NK039(ti)004:439: dur khrod gnas nyul rgya mtsho'i dbus na rol //
NK039(ti)004:440: mi sdug nag po cir yang bsgyur ba'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)004:441: dus bzhi mnga' mdzad chen mo spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)004:443: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK039(ti)004:444: tshur gshegs tshur byon dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:445: bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:446: rnal 'byor gdungs bas bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)004:447: nyi ma byang shar pha ki na //
NK039(ti)004:448: yongs 'dus shing gi rtsa ba na //
NK039(ti)004:449: mtsho mu le mthing gi nang shed na //
NK039(ti)004:450: mthing shun sngon po'i gur khang na //
NK039(ti)004:451: mi mgo rta mgo mkhar du brtsigs //
NK039(ti)004:452: thod pa dgu brtsegs gzhal yas dbus //
NK039(ti)004:453: bse yi sku mkhar gru bzhi'i nang //
NK039(ti)004:454: rin chen sna tshogs pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)004:455: mi ro rta ro gcar du bkram //
NK039(ti)004:456: mi khrag rta khrag 'dam rdzab ldang //
NK039(ti)004:457: de na ma cig lha mo bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:459: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:460: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK039(ti)004:461: ma cig lha mo spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)004:462: byang shar mtshams nas gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:463: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:464: ma yi nang nas ma cig ma //
NK039(ti)004:465: sring gi nang nas sring gcig ma //
NK039(ti)004:466: lha mo chen mo dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)004:467: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)004:468: 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)004:469: chibs su bong bu dmar gwa bcibs //
NK039(ti)004:470: khal du lcags d+r+wa mig dgu 'gel //
NK039(ti)004:471: mchan na nad kyi rkyal pa thogs //
NK039(ti)004:472: g.yas na ral gri sdig pa can //
NK039(ti)004:473: g.yon na gdug pa'i thod khrag thogs //
NK039(ti)004:474: stong gsum kun gyi byos blugs mkhan //
NK039(ti)004:475: gnas ni byang shar mtshams su gnas //
NK039(ti)004:476: rgyug ni bar snang khams su rgyug /
NK039(ti)004:478: rkang la lcags kyi lham gyon ma //
NK039(ti)004:479: sku la mdzes pa'i re lde gsol //
NK039(ti)004:480: ma cig lha mo spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)004:481: ming po rdo rje'i las bcol na //
NK039(ti)004:482: sring mo dam can gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:484: dpal ldan gnyan gyi rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:485: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam gcig ma //
NK039(ti)004:486: lha yi gnas na lha mo nam grub ma //
NK039(ti)004:487: klu yi gnas na klu mo glog 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)004:488: srin gyi nang nas srin mo shams sham ma //
NK039(ti)004:489: mi yi gnas nas bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:490: dgra bgegs bdud la khyod las che ba med //
NK039(ti)004:491: dpal ldan khro mo nam mkha'i klong nas gshegs //
NK039(ti)004:492: mah 'tshubs ma stong du 'khyil pa'i dbus nas gshegs //
NK039(ti)004:493: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba dang //
NK039(ti)004:494: rlung dmar lta bu'i 'tshubs ma ni //
NK039(ti)004:495: sku yi gnas te rgyan gyis mchog /
NK039(ti)004:496: drag shul khyab 'gro glog gi dbang //
NK039(ti)004:497: bsam pa tsam gyis gnas su phyin //
NK039(ti)004:498: ma de'i tshul du gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:499: mah bdud mo dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:500: dam tshig dbang gis spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)004:501: dam las ma 'da' da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)004:502: ma cig dpal ldan re m+aa ti //
NK039(ti)004:503: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum dang bcas //
NK039(ti)004:504: bdag gis gsungs te bos pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)004:505: ma mchis ma thogs myur du byon //
NK039(ti)004:506: mah bos pa'i tshe na snyan ma sra //
NK039(ti)004:507: g.yab pa'i tshe na spyan ma rdul //
NK039(ti)004:508: kyee ma cig lha mo nag mo khyod //
NK039(ti)004:509: sngon tshe phyag na rdo rje la //
NK039(ti)004:510: rang rtags srog gi snying po phul //
NK039(ti)004:511: bos na 'ong bar khas blang bzhin //
NK039(ti)004:512: khas blangs dam la ma 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)004:513: rnal 'byor bdag gis khyod bskul na //
NK039(ti)004:514: dam tshig dbang gis da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)004:515: thugs dam dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:516: rdo rje gdan dang o di ya //
NK039(ti)004:517: byang chub shing dbang bla ma mchog /
NK039(ti)004:518: brgyud par bcas pa'i bsgrub gnas nas //
NK039(ti)004:519: mthu chen 'dod khams dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)004:520: ma cig lha mo 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)004:521: na chung mtshan ldan chur shi ba'i //
NK039(ti)004:522: srin lag g.yab mos spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)004:523: mi dbang smin pa'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)004:524: dam rdzas 'di la myur du byon //
NK039(ti)004:525: b+h+yoh rgya mtsho chen po'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)004:526: lha mo skems ma chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)004:527: ma bdun ma gsum sring mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)004:528: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK039(ti)004:529: ma mo stong dang bdud mo 'bum sde'i 'khor //
NK039(ti)004:530: dril bu'i sgra sgrogs g.yer kha'i phreng ba bcas //
NK039(ti)004:531: dam tshig gnas 'dir smyur du spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)004:532: dur khrod bdag mo mar bcas dzahdzahdzah e a ra
NK039(ti)004:533: li hrim hrim ma h+aa ka li re ma ti
NK039(ti)004:534: sa p+aa ri wa ra sa ma ya dza dzah
NK039(ti)004:535: dzahmh'u bam ho / zhes rol 'bebs pa'i 'ur chems drag po bcas pa'i mthar bzhugs gsol /
NK039(ti)004:536: b+h+yoh bde stong gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK039(ti)004:537: ting 'dzin sprul pa'i gzhal med khang //
NK039(ti)004:539: lcam mo chen mo bzhugs par 'tshal //
NK039(ti)004:540: ma cig dpal ldan re m+aa ti //
NK039(ti)004:541: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum phrag bcas //
NK039(ti)004:542: mi ro gshibs pa'i gdan mchog dang //
NK039(ti)004:543: sprul pa'i bong bu'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:544: 'jigs rung khams gsum za 'dra khros pa'i me //
NK039(ti)004:545: yon por 'khyogs pa'i lce zhag dus mtha'i dbal //
NK039(ti)004:546: ji bzhin mkha' dbyings dogs por byed pa'i dbus //
NK039(ti)004:547: bstan dgrar rngams pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:548: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti rag mo rak+sha
NK039(ti)004:549: ma he ku la pad+ma sa ma ya tish+tha lhan
NK039(ti)004:550: / bzhi pa dbang bskur ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:552: dang po la'ang dngos dang grib sel lo //
NK039(ti)004:554: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK039(ti)004:555: dbang gi lha phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad mdun
NK039(ti)004:556: gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa ma ya dzahs spyan drangs
NK039(ti)004:557: / khyed rnams kyi 'di la mngon par dbang bskur ba stsal du gsol /
NK039(ti)004:559: de'i thugs ka nas rigs kyi yum bzhi bum pa thog pa spros /
NK039(ti)004:560: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka te sa ma ya sh+ri ye h'u /
NK039(ti)004:561: zhes gsungs shing khrus byas pas dri ma thams cad dag /
NK039(ti)004:562: chu yi rgyun gyis sku lus dkar lhag ger gyur /
NK039(ti)004:563: dbang rtags su ral pa'i rtsa ba thod pa bcu drug la mdun nas brtsams te /
NK039(ti)004:564: koo'u ri ma la sogs pa gnas yul gyi ma mo bcu drug gis dbu brgyan par gyur /
NK039(ti)004:566: ma mo'i spyi bor pad+ma dang nyi ma zla ba'i
NK039(ti)004:567: gdan la bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i bcom
NK039(ti)004:568: ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba chen
NK039(ti)004:569: po sku mdog dkar po gangs ri la nyi ma
NK039(ti)004:571: shin tu zhi zhing mdzes la 'dzum pa mtshan dpa'i
NK039(ti)004:572: phung po 'bar ba yab nyid dar gyi chas gos
NK039(ti)004:573: lnga gsol zhing / rdo rje dang dril bu thugs
NK039(ti)004:574: kar bsnol te yum rdo rje snyems ma g.yas yab
NK039(ti)004:575: lnga gsol zhing / la 'khyud cing / g.yon dril
NK039(ti)004:576: bu snyan rtsar 'khrol ba gnyis ka'ang rin po che
NK039(ti)004:577: dang rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa rdo rje'i skyil
NK039(ti)004:578: mo krung gis bzhugs pa la rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK039(ti)004:579: nas de dang 'dra ba spyan drangs badz+ra sa ma
NK039(ti)004:580: ya dzahdzahmh'u bam hoh dbang bskur dri ma dag mi
NK039(ti)004:581: bskyod pas gtso bor byas pa'i rigs lngas dbur brgyan
NK039(ti)004:582: lnga gsol zhing / la 'khyud cing / / bla
NK039(ti)004:583: ma dang dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' khyed kyis
NK039(ti)004:584: dpal ldan lha mo'i sku gsung thugs la dam tshig
NK039(ti)004:585: nyams chag gis grib phog pas 'khon lcug song ba
NK039(ti)004:586: lnga gsol zhing / la 'khyud cing / / dang
NK039(ti)004:587: / bdag gi rgyud kyi nyams chag sgrib ltung thams
NK039(ti)004:588: cad byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol //
NK039(ti)004:589: zhes gsol ba btab pas bla ma'i sku gsung thugs
NK039(ti)004:590: kyi gnas nas yi ge brgya pa'i rang bzhin bdud
NK039(ti)004:591: rtsi dkar dmar mthing gsum 'od zer dang bcas pa
NK039(ti)004:592: byung / rang dang ma mo'i sku lus thams cad gang /
NK039(ti)004:595: mthu stobs nus pa'i gzi byin mchog tu 'bar bar gyur /
NK039(ti)004:596: yi ge brgya pa nyer gcig bzla /
NK039(ti)004:597: mthar rdo rje sems dpa' 'od du zhu nas ma
NK039(ti)004:598: mo la thim par gyur pa'i mthar grib sel bya
NK039(ti)004:599: sel byed thams cad mi dmigs pa'i rang sems nam
NK039(ti)004:600: mkha' lta bu'i ngang la ngal gso ba ni /
NK039(ti)004:601: grib sel thams cad kyi mchog don don dam pa'i grib sel lo //
NK039(ti)004:603: dam bsre ba dam bsgrags pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:605: h'u b+h+yoh rdo rje dri chu bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK039(ti)004:606: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyar /
NK039(ti)004:607: dam tshig dbang gis khrag chen po //
NK039(ti)004:608: bsre ba'i mchog ste srog gi snying //
NK039(ti)004:609: ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs bcas //
NK039(ti)004:610: khyed dang bdag nyid dam basre'o //
NK039(ti)004:611: rtag tu dam las ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)004:612: dam las 'das na bsregs par byed //
NK039(ti)004:613: ma h+aa ku ku sa ma ya pany+tsa a mri ta la kha ram kha hi /
NK039(ti)004:615: dpal ye shes kyi ma mo nag mo chen mo
NK039(ti)004:616: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kun bzang rdo rje 'chang
NK039(ti)004:617: dbang / sprul sku sh+aakya seng ge /
NK039(ti)004:618: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje /
NK039(ti)004:619: slob dpon d+ha na sang+k+ri ta /
NK039(ti)004:622: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK039(ti)004:623: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK039(ti)004:627: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK039(ti)004:629: kun mkhyen dam pa bde gshegs /
NK039(ti)004:630: thugs sras rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK039(ti)004:631: rje byam pa 'bum pa la sogs pa grub thob
NK039(ti)004:632: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma dam
NK039(ti)004:633: pa rnams kyi bka' dang dam tshig bzhin du sangs
NK039(ti)004:637: khyad par dam tshig dang ldan pa bdag cag la ma ltar du brtse bar dgongs /
NK039(ti)004:638: sring ltar du byams pas skyongs /
NK039(ti)004:639: grogs ltar du snying nye zhing /
NK039(ti)004:640: bran ltar du bsgo ba bsgrubs /
NK039(ti)004:641: mdor na sems can gyi don du rnam pa thams
NK039(ti)004:642: cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang bsgrub pa la dus nam
NK039(ti)004:643: du yang g.yel ba med par phrin las rnam pa
NK039(ti)004:644: bzhis rtag tu srungs shing skyobs par mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)004:645: ma mo'i gsang ba'i dam tshig gi rgya bcas /
NK039(ti)004:646: ma h+aa k+aa l+ai de ba'i badz+ra sa ma ya rak+shana tu /
NK039(ti)004:647: gsum pa gsol mchod bya ba'i rim pa la /
NK039(ti)004:651: mthus rdzas ngo mtshar mchod pa spro /
NK039(ti)004:652: gsang mchod thun min mchod pa 'bul /
NK039(ti)004:653: mchod bshags don rnams bsnyen mchod 'bul /
NK039(ti)004:654: zhes rim pa bcu gcig gis dang po ni /
NK039(ti)004:656: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi yum chen mo //
NK039(ti)004:657: rdo rje'i lha mo dpal ldan dbyings phyug ma //
NK039(ti)004:658: ma 'gags thabs kyi rol gar skur ston pa'i //
NK039(ti)004:659: bde mchog kun tu bzang mo rgyal gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:660: rdo rje 'chang sogs bka' drin gter gyi mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:661: 'khor lo'i dbang phyug thugs la mnyam sbyor te //
NK039(ti)004:662: khyod ni ye shes stong pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK039(ti)004:663: rtsa rgyud bla ma mchog tu mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)004:664: bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ni //
NK039(ti)004:665: gnam zhal rgyas 'debs dga' mar ro gcig ma //
NK039(ti)004:666: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho spro bsdu'i 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK039(ti)004:667: yi dam dkyil 'khor mchog tu mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)004:668: gnas gsum ma tshogs kun gyi dbus na brjid //
NK039(ti)004:669: mkha' spyod grong khyer bdag mo sprul pa'i gar //
NK039(ti)004:670: rig lnga 'bum sde'i mkha' 'gro'i dbus bskor bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:671: rdo rje phag mo chen mor mnga' gsol lo //
NK039(ti)004:672: 'byung lnga'i 'od 'khrugs brtsegs pa'i gzhal med na //
NK039(ti)004:673: rta ro gcar bkram mi ro gdan du bting //
NK039(ti)004:674: khrag gi mtsho 'khyil thod pa'i mkhar brtsegs pa //
NK039(ti)004:675: gzhal med gsang ba chen mor stong nyid 'di ni gzugs byad mtshan ma dang /
NK039(ti)004:676: rnam par bral kyang rnam par spros pa'i tshul //
NK039(ti)004:677: 'gags med ngo mtshar shar ba ches mtshar bas /
NK039(ti)004:678: don gyi lha mo chen mor dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyis phyag mdzad cing //
NK039(ti)004:679: 'phags bzhi ma lus 'byung ba'i yum chen mo //
NK039(ti)004:680: gdul bya'i dpal la dpal ldan ma sprul pas //
NK039(ti)004:681: mgon med skyobs ma chen mor sems nyid gzugs dbyibs du ma kha dog gis //
NK039(ti)004:682: spros pas spros med spros pa'i 'jig rung sku //
NK039(ti)004:683: mi zad dus kyi mun ltar ches mnag pa //
NK039(ti)004:684: khams gsum skrag byed chen mor ri yi grib ltar gnyer ba'i khro gnyer nyil /
NK039(ti)004:685: sdang mig yon por bsgyur ba de yis kyang //
NK039(ti)004:686: bdud dpung bye ba thams cad bsregs mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:687: bdud 'joms lha mo chen mor mche gtsigs mi ro rengs za bgegs kyi gshed //
NK039(ti)004:688: a ha ma ma ru ru'i sgra sgrogs shing //
NK039(ti)004:689: snyan cha sbrul nag gser gyi dril bu 'khrol //
NK039(ti)004:690: bgegs 'dul lha mo chen mor srin gyi ral gris phyi rol phyogs nas bstigs //
NK039(ti)004:691: ne'u'i rkyal pas sgrub pa'i re 'dod bskongs //
NK039(ti)004:692: seng ge'i snyan cha 'jigs med rtags su che //
NK039(ti)004:693: srin 'joms lha mo chen mor wa ya wi yi rlung tshub myur mgyogs can //
NK039(ti)004:694: srin bongs dmar po rdzu 'phrul stong gsum spyod //
NK039(ti)004:695: lte bar nyi rgyan spyi bor zla tshes mdzes //
NK039(ti)004:696: chos bsgrub myur skyong chen stong nyid nam mkha'i lus kyi sgeg cing dpa' //
NK039(ti)004:697: khro gtum mche gzengs rngam chen ma ma ni //
NK039(ti)004:698: nu 'dzin dud cing chu 'dzin rab rgyas ma //
NK039(ti)004:699: sgrub pa'i re ba skongs bar zhen med lcags sgrog zhabs kyi gdu bu byas //
NK039(ti)004:700: dga' ba bcu drug thod skom dbu la sgrogs //
NK039(ti)004:701: thod pa'i dbu rgyan rma bya'i mdongs gtsugs ma //
NK039(ti)004:702: dam ldan sring mo chen mor rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan snga nas //
NK039(ti)004:703: chos bzhin bsgrub pa bu gcig ji lta bur //
NK039(ti)004:704: brtse ba'i thugs kyi mi 'dod zhal bzhes pas //
NK039(ti)004:705: rnal 'byor ma ma mchog tu chu skyes bde ba'i 'byung gnas legs bsten nas //
NK039(ti)004:706: bde stong rnal 'byor rdo rje'i dam tshig spel //
NK039(ti)004:707: nang gi phyag rgya dga' bzhi spel ba'i lus //
NK039(ti)004:708: snying grogs phyag rgya chen mor slob dpon la sdang bstan dgra za'o zhes //
NK039(ti)004:709: skan sgra gtogs shing sngon gyi thugs dam la //
NK039(ti)004:710: brel bas rgyugs ma dam tshig ma mo ni //
NK039(ti)004:711: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bran der zhing bcu tshangs ba gang la gtad pa rnams //
NK039(ti)004:712: brtse ba'i thugs des 'khor bar mi gtong slad //
NK039(ti)004:713: khros pa'i zhal gyis dum bur 'dral mdzad pas //
NK039(ti)004:714: bstan dgra 'joms ma chen mor dkon mchog gsum gyi dbu 'phang bstod pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:715: dben gnas chos 'khor skyongs la thugs rjes pas //
NK039(ti)004:716: bka' srung kun gyi gtso mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)004:717: dus gsum rgyal ba'i bstan srungs sbrul gdug tshangs ltar 'jigs rung 'khor ba 'dir //
NK039(ti)004:718: rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i snang tshul la //
NK039(ti)004:719: zhen med nges 'byung bsgom rnams skyongs mdzad mas //
NK039(ti)004:720: tshul khrims lha mo chen mor bdag gzhan don du thugs bskyed mi nyams shing //
NK039(ti)004:721: mkha' mtha' klas pa'i 'gro ba byang chub tu //
NK039(ti)004:722: 'god 'dod rgyal sras spyod ma'i mgon skyobs mdzad //
NK039(ti)004:723: gzhan phan lha mo chen mor rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig 'du ba'i sgor //
NK039(ti)004:724: dpal ldan rgyud sde rnams kyi mnga' bdag gi //
NK039(ti)004:725: skal bzang bu la rtag tu skyongs mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:726: rgyud sde'i srung ma chen mor kyee /
NK039(ti)004:727: chos dbyings chos 'byung yangs pa'i gzhal med na //
NK039(ti)004:728: rtsa brgyud bla ma'i bsgo ba bsgrub mdzad de //
NK039(ti)004:729: lha mo chen mo ma mo k+aa lir grags //
NK039(ti)004:730: sngon gyi thugs dam 'jigs rung rlabs su che //
NK039(ti)004:731: tsit+ta dmar la rtag tu rngams rol ma //
NK039(ti)004:732: lha chen dpal 'bar srid gsum bdag mo khyed //
NK039(ti)004:733: bstan dgra 'joms mdzad gshed chen dam ldan ni //
NK039(ti)004:734: sprul pa'i sprin dpung mkha' dang mnyam spro bar //
NK039(ti)004:735: thugs dam 'gyur med chos sku'i cho rol las //
NK039(ti)004:736: rang rig ye shes spros las 'das pa'i 'dzum //
NK039(ti)004:737: brjod med brjod pa kun stong sems kyi gshis //
NK039(ti)004:738: yin lugs cir yang 'char ba'i rig pa'i 'phrul //
NK039(ti)004:739: lha mchog stobs ldan dpa' mor mnga' gsol nas //
NK039(ti)004:740: phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK039(ti)004:741: dge legs bkra shis gdugs bzang 'khor yug tu //
NK039(ti)004:742: rgyal bstan kun khyab chen po'i bkra shis shog /
NK039(ti)004:744: b+h+yoh nag mo khrag 'thung rdo rje ral pa can //
NK039(ti)004:745: dbang chen rdo rje thog dang ser ba 'bebs //
NK039(ti)004:746: khams gsum sgrol mdzad srid gsum rtsad nas gcod //
NK039(ti)004:747: ral pa bsigs pas stong gsum kun tu khyab //
NK039(ti)004:748: mche ba gtsigs pas dgra bgegs zhal du 'dren //
NK039(ti)004:749: ma lus dbang du bsdud la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:750: ma gcig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:751: nag mo chen mo rnal 'byor ma //
NK039(ti)004:752: pho nya bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs la //
NK039(ti)004:753: bdag gis dad pa'i phyag bagyi'o //
NK039(ti)004:754: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti a ti p+au ho /
NK039(ti)004:757: b+h+yoh ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:758: phyag brnyan bran g.yog 'khor dang bcas //
NK039(ti)004:760: bu yis mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:762: rgya mtsho 'bab chu chu mig rdzing //
NK039(ti)004:764: ma yi sku la thim gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:765: thugs mchog dam pa mnyes gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:766: dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)004:767: ma h+aa ka li de wi re ma ti ar+g+ham +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)004:768: yan lag brgyad ldang rdzing bu dang //
NK039(ti)004:769: dug gis sbyar ba drag po'i chu //
NK039(ti)004:770: ma yi zhabs bsil phyir du 'bul //
NK039(ti)004:771: thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa k+aa li de wi re ma ti pa d+yam +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)004:772: chu skyes thang skyes me tog dang //
NK039(ti)004:773: dbang po lnga yi me tog 'di //
NK039(ti)004:774: ma yi dbu la thugs mchog dngos grub pash+pe ga bur gla rtsi gurguma dang //
NK039(ti)004:775: sha chen spos kyi dud pa 'di //
NK039(ti)004:776: ma yi shangs la thugs mchog dngos grub d+hush+pe nyi zla glog dang gsal ba'i sgron //
NK039(ti)004:777: zhun chen mdangs kyi mar me 'di //
NK039(ti)004:778: ma yi spyan la thim gyur thugs mchog dngos grub a lko khrag chen dug dang sbyar ba yi //
NK039(ti)004:780: ma yi thugs kar thugs mchog dngos grub gan+d+he phye ma lnga yi bshos bu dang //
NK039(ti)004:781: nal sha yon tan lnga ldan 'di //
NK039(ti)004:782: ma yi ljags la thugs mchog dngos grub nee wid+ya /
NK039(ti)004:783: pi wam gling bu mkhar ba'i rnga //
NK039(ti)004:784: man 'gal cha lang rkang gi dung //
NK039(ti)004:785: ma yi snyan la thugs mchog dngos grub shab+ta +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)004:788: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:789: ma khyed la gzugs kyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:790: lha mo'i gzugs dang klu mo'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)004:791: bzang ba'i gzugs dang brjid pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)004:792: kha dog sna tshogs mdzes pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)004:793: cir yang bsgyur ba'i gzugs la sogs //
NK039(ti)004:794: ma cig spyan la thugs mchog dngos grub ma h+aa r+au pa +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)004:795: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:796: ma khyod la sgra yi mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:797: pi wam gling bu mkhar ba'i rnga //
NK039(ti)004:798: rdza rnga cha lang gan+de dung //
NK039(ti)004:799: cang te'u sil snyan la sogs te //
NK039(ti)004:800: dril bu rnga dbyang sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)004:801: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK039(ti)004:802: ma cig snyan la thugs mchog dngos grub shap+ta ma
NK039(ti)004:803: cig lha mo ma khyed la dri yi mchod a
NK039(ti)004:804: ka ru dang du ru ka /
NK039(ti)004:805: sha ka rahdang lnga sbyar ba'i //
NK039(ti)004:806: tsan+da dkar dmar dri spos chab //
NK039(ti)004:807: ma gcig thugs kar thugs mchog dngos grub gan+d+he ma
NK039(ti)004:808: cig lha mo ma khyod la ro yi mchod pa
NK039(ti)004:809: 'bul ba ni // lha yis zhal zas bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK039(ti)004:810: ma yi ljags thugs mchog dngos grub dam pa ra
NK039(ti)004:811: sa ma cig lha mo ma khyed la reg bya'i
NK039(ti)004:813: lha rdzas pany+tsa li ka'i dar //
NK039(ti)004:814: stag glang zhing gi shun pa bcas //
NK039(ti)004:815: ma cig sku thugs mchog dngos grub par+she ma cig
NK039(ti)004:816: lha mo dpal ma khyed la chos kyi mchod pa
NK039(ti)004:817: 'bul sna tshogs snang khams thams cad kun //
NK039(ti)004:818: zag med bde stong ye shes dngos //
NK039(ti)004:819: ma mnyam pa nyid du rol gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:820: ma h+aa ka li de wi re ma ti d+harma +aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)004:822: b+h+yoh ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor bcas la //
NK039(ti)004:823: yang cig mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:824: mi dbang smin pa'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)004:825: 'chi ka'i mtshal tig dmar po dang //
NK039(ti)004:826: shing lo rlung khyer sar ma lhung //
NK039(ti)004:827: 'bras bu smin pa'i shing tog dang //
NK039(ti)004:828: na chung mo yi byung zad khrag /
NK039(ti)004:829: ma nyams byang sems dkar dmar dang //
NK039(ti)004:830: gri rgod snying dang dbang po lnga //
NK039(ti)004:831: bong bu'i snying dang khrims 'chal sha /
NK039(ti)004:832: rnam lnga bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'di //
NK039(ti)004:834: bstan pa srung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:835: ma h+aa k+aa li de wi re ma ti sa p+aa ri wa ra +aahka ro //
NK039(ti)004:838: b+h+yoh rab yangs nam mkha' gang ba'i mchod sprin ni //
NK039(ti)004:839: dpag par dka' ba sgyu ma lta bu'i mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:840: thogs med ting 'dzin blo yis legs phyes te //
NK039(ti)004:841: phyogs kyi 'khor lo dogs por byed bzhin 'bul //
NK039(ti)004:842: ting 'dzin sil gyis legs par bris pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)004:843: rten 'brel 'dzum dkar bsu ba'i smin legs can //
NK039(ti)004:844: yid 'phrog dga' ba'i nyams brgyar 'char ba'i ma //
NK039(ti)004:845: rin chen gzhong thog phreng ba'i do shal 'phyang //
NK039(ti)004:846: mdzes pa'i gar dang snyan pa'i glu bsgyur ba'i //
NK039(ti)004:847: mu tig do shal legs 'dzin 'khrol bcas te //
NK039(ti)004:848: snang stong bkod pa'i mig mang brtse ba can //
NK039(ti)004:849: gcig las du mar 'phrul ba 'byung gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:850: gser sbyangs 'khor lo rtsib stong 'od du 'bar //
NK039(ti)004:851: rin chen lha rdzas zur brgyad 'dod kun 'byung //
NK039(ti)004:852: skyon bral yid kyi brtan 'phrog bud med mchog /
NK039(ti)004:853: bsam pa'i don bsgrub blon po rin po che //
NK039(ti)004:854: gangs ri ltar dkar glang chen stobs dang ldan //
NK039(ti)004:855: 'gros bzang mdog sdug cang shes rta yi mchog /
NK039(ti)004:856: phas rgol dgra las rnam rgyal dmag dpon dang //
NK039(ti)004:857: gdugs dkar stong ldan d+r+wa ba phyogs brgyar 'khor //
NK039(ti)004:858: drang zhing ldan pa'i mi nub rgyal mtshan brtan //
NK039(ti)004:859: zab cing khug mang dpal gyi be'u lhas //
NK039(ti)004:860: grags snyan ring du 'khrol ba skye lnga pa //
NK039(ti)004:861: sna tshogs mdog bzang ngo mtshar pad+ma'i tshal //
NK039(ti)004:862: shes rab gser mig 'khyil pa rab tu mdzes //
NK039(ti)004:863: dzam+bu'i pur wa na yi 'khor lo brtan //
NK039(ti)004:864: 'dod 'byung bum bzang zad med gter gyi mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:865: ma 'dres gzugs brgya gsal ba'i a dar+sha //
NK039(ti)004:866: chos dung dam pa'i dbyangs snyan mngon par mdzes //
NK039(ti)004:867: g+hi ham nad 'joms bdud rtsi'i 'chi med sman //
NK039(ti)004:868: durba lo bzang phang phang kun tu dkrigs //
NK039(ti)004:869: 'dod 'jo'i ba bzang zho yi snying po can //
NK039(ti)004:870: bilba 'bras bu bzang 'dod pa'i ro bda' ba //
NK039(ti)004:871: li khri bzang ma dbang gi rdzas chen po //
NK039(ti)004:872: bgegs 'joms nyungs dkar rdo rje'i rigs kyi gnas //
NK039(ti)004:873: zad med nam mkha' mdzad kyi 'khor lo 'bul //
NK039(ti)004:874: ma h+aa k+aa li de wi re ma ti sa pa ri wa ra rat+na mang+ga la p+au dzah+aahmh'u /
NK039(ti)004:875: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas 'bul /
NK039(ti)004:876: bdun pa la sman gtor rak+ta gsum gyi /
NK039(ti)004:879: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK039(ti)004:880: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK039(ti)004:881: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK039(ti)004:882: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK039(ti)004:883: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK039(ti)004:884: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK039(ti)004:885: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)004:886: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen dang //
NK039(ti)004:887: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK039(ti)004:888: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen dang //
NK039(ti)004:889: lha dang lha min gsang ba yi //
NK039(ti)004:890: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK039(ti)004:891: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK039(ti)004:892: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK039(ti)004:893: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid las //
NK039(ti)004:894: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK039(ti)004:895: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK039(ti)004:896: phul ba'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)004:897: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ar+g+ham
NK039(ti)004:898: pra ti tsa hoh khyab bdag drug pa rtsa ba'i
NK039(ti)004:899: bla ma'i bar // bka' brgyud bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor la //
NK039(ti)004:900: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung mar bcas //
NK039(ti)004:901: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i thugs rjes na ma sarba rdo
NK039(ti)004:902: rje lha mo nag mo mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal
NK039(ti)004:903: // dus gsum sangs rgyas kun dang spyod yul gcig pa'i yum //
NK039(ti)004:904: khams gsum log par blta ba thams cad dbyings su sgrol //
NK039(ti)004:905: srid gsum log 'dren za ba'i yul rnams la //
NK039(ti)004:906: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rjes brtse dgongs na ma
NK039(ti)004:907: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a
NK039(ti)004:908: mri ta la kha ram kha hih b+h+yoh khyod kyi
NK039(ti)004:909: g.yog mo srin mo chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)004:910: ma mo bdun dang ma gsum sring mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)004:911: seng stag 'brug spyang gdong mo bzhi rnams la //
NK039(ti)004:912: rnam dag thugs rjes na ma sarba dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK039(ti)004:913: 'khor gyi ma mo stong dang rtsa brgyad dang //
NK039(ti)004:914: gzhan yang bdud mo bye ba 'bum sde'i 'khor //
NK039(ti)004:915: mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro ma sring rgya mtsho la //
NK039(ti)004:916: rnam dag thugs rjes na ma sarba h'u b+h+yoh ma cig nag mo chen mo 'khor bcas rnams //
NK039(ti)004:917: dngos grub rtsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)004:918: ma yis bu la dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)004:919: ye shes gsang ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)004:920: 'dod khams 'dul ba'i 'jig rten dbang bsdud ye shes
NK039(ti)004:921: lnga yi tshe bsod rgyas pa'i bdud rtsi sman gyi
NK039(ti)004:922: grub chen brgyad kyi phrin las rnam bzhi'i sku gsung
NK039(ti)004:923: thugs kyi sh+r+ai de wi ma h+aa k+aa li re
NK039(ti)004:926: sarba sid+d+hi h+r+aih gnyis pa ni /
NK039(ti)004:928: ma mo chags pas bzhugs par bsam nas b+ha ling 'bul te /
NK039(ti)004:930: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las gtor ma'i steng 'dod yon gyi lha mo bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho //
NK039(ti)004:931: 'og sha khrag rus pa'i gram khrod chen por gyur /
NK039(ti)004:933: ma cig lha mo dpal lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:934: rdo rje lha mo nag mo che //
NK039(ti)004:935: gtor ma'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:936: ma cig thugs dam zhal zas snod //
NK039(ti)004:937: me rlung dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i steng //
NK039(ti)004:938: p+aa las b+han+d+ha bcud yangs pa'i //
NK039(ti)004:940: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:941: rdzongs dang bka' bzlog nag mo che //
NK039(ti)004:942: gsol lo rol gcig dgyes par mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:943: ma cig lha mo ma cig thugs dam zhal zas snod //
NK039(ti)004:944: bsad pa'i sha dang myos pa'i chang //
NK039(ti)004:945: bsreg pa'i gsur dang rlon pa'i sha /
NK039(ti)004:946: btsos pa'i sha dang khu ba khrag /
NK039(ti)004:947: nang rol glo snying mkhal mar bcas //
NK039(ti)004:949: b+h+yoh rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)004:950: bum dang ril dang phyed tsal dang //
NK039(ti)004:951: nang rol glo snying mkhal ma bcas //
NK039(ti)004:952: sha dang rus pa rkang tshil rnams //
NK039(ti)004:954: bstan pa srungs phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:955: ma cig lha mo ma khyed la yid bzhin mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:956: 'bras bu lnga yi tshom bu bdud rtsi dang //
NK039(ti)004:957: ko ra tsa na dang ni dri chen thal chen dang //
NK039(ti)004:958: ma h+aa mam sa rak+ta tsit+ta ba su ta //
NK039(ti)004:959: ma cig zhal du thugs mchog dngos grub gsol lo rol cig dgongs shig sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)004:960: ru ru bish+tha be d+h+wa pi dri tsa pa la
NK039(ti)004:961: a shug+me h'u b+h+yo dza dza kha ram kha hi
NK039(ti)004:962: / 'byung po'i phung po la kha ram ma mo nag mo bee t+aa li ku lu ku lu /
NK039(ti)004:964: ma h+aa mam sa ma h+aa tsit+ta ma h+aa ba su ta /
NK039(ti)004:965: ma h+aa ko ro tsa na dgra bgegs kyi dbang
NK039(ti)004:966: po rnam lnga la ra rgya ram pa la shig
NK039(ti)004:969: b+h+yoh ma cig lha mo bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs bcas //
NK039(ti)004:970: thugs dam dbang gis snying khrag dmar la rol //
NK039(ti)004:971: ma cig khrag 'thung dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)004:972: dam rdzas rmad du byung ba'i dmar chen bzhes //
NK039(ti)004:973: ma h+aa rak+ta la kha hi /
NK039(ti)004:975: b+h+yoh sems nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i rol pa las //
NK039(ti)004:976: mchod dang mchod par bya ba gnyis su med //
NK039(ti)004:977: dpe dang yi ge kha dog tshig las 'das //
NK039(ti)004:978: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du rang gi sems //
NK039(ti)004:979: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med rol pa las //
NK039(ti)004:980: bde chen byang chub sems kyi phrin las ni //
NK039(ti)004:981: zad med bde stong rol pa'i mchod pa ste //
NK039(ti)004:982: mchod pa thams cad chos kyi dbyings su dag /
NK039(ti)004:984: b+h+yoh bskal pa me rlung 'tshubs ma'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)004:985: ma cig lha mo nag mo glo 'gyu ma //
NK039(ti)004:986: pho nya bdud kyi bu mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)004:987: ma cig 'khor bcas brtse bas bdag la dgongs //
NK039(ti)004:988: bdag nyid mi mkhas rmongs pa'i dbang gyur te //
NK039(ti)004:989: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gis //
NK039(ti)004:990: dam tshig nyams chag 'gal 'khrul gyur pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:991: ting 'dzin mi gsal ra ri kha khol dang /
NK039(ti)004:992: sngags dang phyag rgya gra chags zur nyams dang //
NK039(ti)004:993: nyams pa can gyi grib kyis phog pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:994: phud nyams lhag mar gyur pa thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)004:995: dam rdzas mchod rdzas dus su ma tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)004:996: dpon g.yogs mched lcam thugs dang 'gal ba dang //
NK039(ti)004:997: khyad par ma cig dpal ldan lha mo yi //
NK039(ti)004:998: sku gsung thugs dang rtsa ba yan lag gis //
NK039(ti)004:999: dam tshig nyams chag 'gal 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)004:1000: ma cig bdud mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams la bshags //
NK039(ti)004:1001: rab tu bshags so tshang pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)004:1003: b+h+yoh dpal ldan lha mo dpal 'bar nag mo ni //
NK039(ti)004:1004: rang don spangs te 'khor ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK039(ti)004:1005: dpag par dka' ba'i rnam 'phrul cir yang ston //
NK039(ti)004:1006: kun tu bzang mo rdo rje dbyings phyug ma /
NK039(ti)004:1008: 1 / gsang ba ye shes mkha' 'gro yongs kyi gtso //
NK039(ti)004:1009: sprul pas stong khams ma lus 'gengs byed ma //
NK039(ti)004:1010: khyod ni sher phyin yum dang gnyis med kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1011: tshul ston thabs mkhas las tshul cir yang ston /
NK039(ti)004:1013: 2 / gser thub bstan la lha mo long gtong gis //
NK039(ti)004:1014: dge bcu spyad pas drag pa'i sras mor 'khrungs //
NK039(ti)004:1015: mar me mdzad bstan dge slong dbang phyug sder //
NK039(ti)004:1016: mchod pas sangs rgyas don kun grub pa mjal /
NK039(ti)004:1018: 3 / 'od srung bstan la zhe sdang spyod pa'i mthus //
NK039(ti)004:1019: srin po'i chung ma rang lceb sdug bsngal bar //
NK039(ti)004:1020: ston kyang don la ye shes mkha' 'gro ste //
NK039(ti)004:1021: ye shes sgyu ma'i rol pa cir yang 'char /
NK039(ti)004:1023: 4 / rdo rje gdan du sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK039(ti)004:1024: bdud rtsi brnyes tshe srog gi snying po phul //
NK039(ti)004:1025: bstan pa srungs ba'i g.yar dam mnos pas kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1026: sa brgyad thob cing lung bstan brnyes gyur pa /
NK039(ti)004:1028: 5 / dpal ldan rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i bstan srung ma //
NK039(ti)004:1029: 'dod khams dbang mo drag shul mthu chen rol //
NK039(ti)004:1030: ye shes 'jig rten ma mo'i 'khor bcas te //
NK039(ti)004:1031: dam tshig can skyongs khyed la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)004:1032: b+h+yoh skal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK039(ti)004:1033: rlung nag dgu klong 'khrigs pa'i pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)004:1034: ma cig lha mo 'dod khams gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)004:1035: nag mo za byed 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK039(ti)004:1036: mthing nag mi srun khrag gi ral pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1037: mah khyed kyi sku mdog nag mo ston pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1038: don dam dbyings na bskyed pa med pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1039: ral pa g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyil pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1040: yum gyi mkha' las sprul pa 'byed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1041: ral pa'i gseb nas me stag 'phro ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1042: thugs rje'i sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1043: ral pa spyi bo'i gtsug tu 'khyil ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1044: thugs dam dgongs spyod gcig tu mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1045: thod skom phreng bas dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1046: thugs rjes sprul pa'i 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1047: rma bya'i rgyal mtshan dbu la gtsugs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1048: phrin las rnam bzhi so sor mdzad pa'i snyan cha g.yas na seng ge 'gying ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1049: dman mo thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i snyan g.yon sbrul nag gdeng ka 'phyo ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1050: zhe sdang ma spangs dbyings su dag pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1051: snyan cha gser gyi dril bu 'khrol ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1052: sangs rgyas kun la bsnyen bskur mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1053: spyan rtsa dmar po phyogs bcur gzigs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1054: rnal 'byor srid gsum bya ra mdzad shang nas nad kyi rlangs pa 'thul ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1055: sdang ba'i dgra la nad yams 'beb pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1056: zhal gyi hom khung drag por gdengs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1057: dam rdzas gang yin zhal du gsol ba'i rno gdug mche ba zur gsum gtsigs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1058: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'i sha la rol pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1059: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la mnab pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1060: chos nyid yang dag don dang ldan pa'i sku smad glang chen ko rlon gsol ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1061: theg pa mchog gi don dang ldan pa'i snam phye re lde nag pos dkris pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1062: 'jig rten 'di na che btsan ldan pa'i spyi bo'i gtsug na zla rgyas gsal ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1063: ma rig mun pa dbyings su dag pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1064: lte ba'i dbus na nyi ma shar ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1065: srid pa'i rgya mtsho gting nas skem pa'i stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1066: drag po'i cha lugs mngon du gyur pa'i phyag g.yas gdug pa'i ral gri 'phyar ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1067: dgra bgegs skye rgyud rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyag g.yon b+han+d+ha dmar chen bsnams pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1068: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal khrag ltar 'thung ba'i mchan na ne'u'i rkyal pa thogs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1069: bsgrub pa po la dngos grub ster ba'i zhabs la dbang gi lcags sgrog sgrogs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1070: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i phyir phyogs dril gyi pha la bcibs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1071: log par lta ba'i dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i srin po'i ya 'gal snga ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1072: srin yul lang+ka p+au rir bsgrod pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1073: srin mo'i man 'gal phyi ru byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1074: srin khams ma lus dbang du bsdud pa'i gong thag glo smad sprul la byas pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1075: zhe sdang sdug pa can rnams 'dul ba'i rus sbal nag po'i phog gus btab pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1076: klu bdud ma rungs dam la 'dogs pa'i snga shad bdud kyi khram bam bkal ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1077: dam nyams dgra bo khram la 'debs pa'i phyi shad nad kyi rkyal pa bkal ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1078: dam nyams dgra la nad yams 'bebs pa'i don dam bcud kyi rtags su zhag gi zo ris brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1079: thugs rje'i chags pa'i rtags su rak+ta'i thig le'i brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1080: 'dul byed phrin las rtags su thal ba'i tshom bus byugs //
NK039(ti)004:1081: 'bum phrag ma mo'i 'khor gyis rab tu bskor ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1082: stong gsum kun tu khyab pa'i phrin las mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK039(ti)004:1083: b+h+yoh ma cig kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho chen po skems //
NK039(ti)004:1084: lag na rdo rje 'phen pa'i ri rab sil bur bsnyil //
NK039(ti)004:1085: mthu chen sprin gyi shugs 'chang glog ltar myur mgyogs pa //
NK039(ti)004:1086: lha mo dpal ldan khyed la bdag gis btsun par bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1087: b+h+yoh dpal ldan ma chen cir yang sprul pa las //
NK039(ti)004:1088: 'khor gyi ma mo srid gsum khyab pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1089: khyod dang ye nas dam tshig gci ga pa yin //
NK039(ti)004:1090: skem ma sngon nas 'gro la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1091: 'jig rten stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)004:1092: rgya mtsho hub kyis rngub pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1093: ri rab dpang du 'debs nus pa //
NK039(ti)004:1094: ma bdun ma gsum sring mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)004:1095: seng stag 'brug spyang gdong mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)004:1096: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK039(ti)004:1097: ma mo stong dang 'bum sde'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)004:1098: bye ba sprul pa'i bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)004:1099: drag shul rol pa bsam mi khyab //
NK039(ti)004:1100: phrin las rnam bzhi'i rol pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1101: dam tshig 'dod dgur bsgyur ba yi //
NK039(ti)004:1102: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)004:1103: rdo rje dbyings phyug rig ma ni //
NK039(ti)004:1104: log rtog gzhoms pa'i dpa' bo la //
NK039(ti)004:1105: ma chen dpal lhar mtshan gsol ba //
NK039(ti)004:1106: yum chen khyed la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)004:1107: b+h+yoh dpal ldan lha mo mthu chen khyod //
NK039(ti)004:1108: chos skyong rgyal mo mi zad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1109: gsang ba dbyings phyug mkha' 'gro ma //
NK039(ti)004:1110: bstan srungs mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1111: lha mo klu mo gnod sbyin mo //
NK039(ti)004:1112: grul bum dri za 'byung po dang //
NK039(ti)004:1113: cir yang sprul pa'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK039(ti)004:1114: ming brgya ma la mtshan stong ma //
NK039(ti)004:1115: rgyal bstan rgyas mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1116: dngos grub ster mdzad ma la phrin las bsgrub mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1117: dgra bgegs 'dul mdzad ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1118: bcu gcig pa bsnyen pa 'bul ba la spyir dbul ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:1121: rang nyid yi dam gyi thugs ka'i h'u gis mthar bskor yi dam sngags kyis g.yas su bskor ba /
NK039(ti)004:1122: de yi mthar lha mo'i sngags kyis bskor bar gyur
NK039(ti)004:1123: par bsam nas yi dam gyi bsnyen mthar sngags bdun
NK039(ti)004:1125: dam tshig gi sems dpa' mdun gyi ma mo'i thugs
NK039(ti)004:1126: kar ha las ye shes sems dpa'i lha mo koo
NK039(ti)004:1128: g.yas zhing dbyug g.yon thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)004:1129: de yi thugs kar zla ba'i steng du ting 'dzin sems dpa' ral gri /
NK039(ti)004:1130: de'i so yu'i mtshams su ma nag mo gcig la yi ge bco lngas bskor bas /
NK039(ti)004:1131: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod pa'i tshul du spros pas dgyes pa bskyed /
NK039(ti)004:1132: de'i ma yig sngags phreng dang bcas pa'i 'od zer
NK039(ti)004:1133: gyis ci 'dod pa'i las rab 'byams bsgrub nas thugs
NK039(ti)004:1134: ka'i sa bon la thim pas ma mo'i nus mthu
NK039(ti)004:1135: bdag gis thob par bsam la /
NK039(ti)004:1136: ru ru ro ru tsa pa la a shug+me h'u
NK039(ti)004:1137: b+h+yohdzahdzah yi ge bco lnga pa 'di rtsa sngags so
NK039(ti)004:1138: // gnyis pa la brten tshul bzhi'i bsnyen dmigs dang /
NK039(ti)004:1139: 'bod rbad bsad gsum gyis sgrub pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:1140: srog gi las brgyad kyi dmigs rim mo //
NK039(ti)004:1141: dang po la bzhi las ma ltar du bsten pa ni /
NK039(ti)004:1142: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros lha mo'i thugs kar phog /
NK039(ti)004:1143: lha mo'i thugs ka'i sngags phreng las sngags phreng gnyis pa zhig byung /
NK039(ti)004:1144: bde ldan lha mo brnyes nas thugs ka'i nu 'bur
NK039(ti)004:1145: nas tshur la sngags phreng gi dngos grub stsol bar
NK039(ti)004:1146: bsam nas / gtso mo'i srog snying /
NK039(ti)004:1147: ru ru be tista ba do si ru ru ro
NK039(ti)004:1148: ru be tish+tha ba do pi tsa pa la a
NK039(ti)004:1149: shug+me h'uhb+h+yohdzah 'od zer des 'khor rnams kyang las la
NK039(ti)004:1150: bskul bar gyur / khol mo re ti chu srin gdong srog snying /
NK039(ti)004:1153: rag+mo tsit+ta kha rag+mo h'u b+h+yoh ma ma traka rak+sha /
NK039(ti)004:1154: kha mun dra ba dra rak+sha tsit+ta kha rag ma /
NK039(ti)004:1155: re ma ti sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)004:1156: bra ma ma h+aa ste pran dun b+h+yo ru lu
NK039(ti)004:1157: ru lu b+h+yo dza dzah 'khor ma mo thams cad
NK039(ti)004:1158: kyi snying po / sa ma ya du ling rak+sha si /
NK039(ti)004:1163: m+aa m+aa m+aa m+aa ru lu ru lu /
NK039(ti)004:1166: gnyis pa sring ltar bsten pa /
NK039(ti)004:1167: rang gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer 'phros /
NK039(ti)004:1170: bde bar gshegs pa sras bcas mchod /
NK039(ti)004:1174: lha mo'i sku gsung thugs mnyes /
NK039(ti)004:1175: dngos grub rnams lte ba nas byung /
NK039(ti)004:1176: rang gi snying khar 'od zer rab tu 'khor ba'i rnam par gyur pa bsgom mthar /
NK039(ti)004:1177: ma h+aa ka li re ma ti /
NK039(ti)004:1178: ma ma ru lu rak+sha re ma ti /
NK039(ti)004:1179: ma ma ru lu rak+sha re ma ti /
NK039(ti)004:1180: ru lu ru lu b+h+yohdzahdzah snying po'o //
NK039(ti)004:1181: gsum pa mdza' mo'i chung ma ltar bsten pa /
NK039(ti)004:1182: bdag gi thugs las 'phros pa'i sngags kyi 'od zer rtsa dbu ma'i nang nas mar zhugs /
NK039(ti)004:1183: gsang ba'i rdo rje nas phyir phyung /
NK039(ti)004:1185: mchod pa sna tshogs kyis mchod nas brnyes shing tshims /
NK039(ti)004:1187: thugs ka nas zhal brgyud tshur byung bdag gi zhal
NK039(ti)004:1188: du zhugs pas dngos grub sna tshogs ster bar gyur
NK039(ti)004:1189: pa'i mthar 'gal me'i 'khor lo ltar bsgom ste /
NK039(ti)004:1190: trag rak+sha ma hi dun b+h+yoh ma h+aa yak+sha t+aik+na k+aa li dun b+h+yoh yang snying bcu bdun ma'o //
NK039(ti)004:1191: bzhi pa bran ltar bsten pa /
NK039(ti)004:1192: bdag gi thugs ka'i sngags 'od zer bcas pa lha mo'i thugs kar phog /
NK039(ti)004:1193: ma mo mnyes shing sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub
NK039(ti)004:1194: thams cad ma mo'i zhal nas 'od zer gyi rnam
NK039(ti)004:1195: par rang gi zhal du zhugs te snying kar 'khor
NK039(ti)004:1197: trak+sha ma ma ma ti dun b+h+yoh ma h+aa rak+sha
NK039(ti)004:1198: ma h+aa tik+sh+na nag mo dun ting ma b+h+yoh nyer
NK039(ti)004:1200: gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i man ngag /
NK039(ti)004:1201: rang yi dam gyi thugs ka nas h'u gi 'od
NK039(ti)004:1202: zer gyis mdun du gnas pa'i lha mo'i thugs ka'i
NK039(ti)004:1203: ma la thim zhing yongs su bskul bas nyi ma
NK039(ti)004:1205: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas slar yang /
NK039(ti)004:1206: ma mo 'khor dang bcas pa bkug /
NK039(ti)004:1207: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che'i tshul bzhin bsgrub
NK039(ti)004:1208: pa la sdang ba'i dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad
NK039(ti)004:1209: / gnod pa'i bgegs ma lus pa thal ba'i rdul phran bzhin du brlag /
NK039(ti)004:1210: phrin las 'dod dgu yid bzhin du bsgrub par bsam nas /
NK039(ti)004:1211: ru ru tsa rur a shug+me /
NK039(ti)004:1212: pra ti ru dra pra kha shag rak+mo h'u /
NK039(ti)004:1216: ru ru pe ru re h'u /
NK039(ti)004:1218: rag+mo rnying kha la rag+mo thun b+h+yo dzahdzah rbad pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:1219: ru lu re ma ti sa ma ya /
NK039(ti)004:1221: pra ma rag+mo ru lu ru lu b+h+yo dzahdzah kha
NK039(ti)004:1222: rag de khem dzahdzah kha le thun b+h+yo thun ma
NK039(ti)004:1223: mo b+h+yo / h'u rag+mo ni sha ku ru rbad /
NK039(ti)004:1224: rag+mo ar+ya dzahdzah ti khem kha le b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)004:1225: sa ma ya dgra bgegs ma ra ya h'u phatah bsad pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:1227: dbab dang dam btags srog skor ba /
NK039(ti)004:1228: gcun dang yang rig blang ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:1229: gzer ba gzi byin blang ba dang /
NK039(ti)004:1230: zil gyis mnan pa rnam pa brgyad /
NK039(ti)004:1231: ces gsung ste shin tu gnyan pas gzhung du ma bkod pa be'u bum las shes par bya'o //
NK039(ti)004:1232: bcu gcig pa las bsnyen mchod dngos dang /
NK039(ti)004:1235: sh+ri de wi ma h+aa k+aa li ma ma sa
NK039(ti)004:1236: p+aa ri wa ra badz+ra ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ye s+w+aa
NK039(ti)004:1237: h+aahns / shap+ta'i bar gyis mchod cing rol mo bya /
NK039(ti)004:1241: mah rig pa rang byung gi rgyal mo /
NK039(ti)004:1242: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo /
NK039(ti)004:1243: dus bzhis lha mos sku la brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)004:1246: 'dod pa khams kyi dbang phyug ma sngon du rgyugs pa chu srin mgo can /
NK039(ti)004:1247: ma mo bdun dang ma gsum sring mo rnam bzhi /
NK039(ti)004:1248: rjes su rgyug cing g.yas g.yon myul ba /
NK039(ti)004:1249: nyi zla stong gis khyab par 'gro ma /
NK039(ti)004:1250: gdong mo chen mo seng stag 'brug spyang bzhi /
NK039(ti)004:1251: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK039(ti)004:1252: ma mo nag mo stong gi tshogs dang /
NK039(ti)004:1253: bdud mo bye ba 'bum sde'i bka' 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK039(ti)004:1254: mthu chen dam pa chos skyong ba'i srung ma'i dbang po rnams la /
NK039(ti)004:1255: mchod cing gser skyes phud kyis gsol lo //
NK039(ti)004:1256: kun mkhyen sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che
NK039(ti)004:1257: bshad dang sgrub pa'i sgo nas 'jig rten gyi khams
NK039(ti)004:1258: 'dir yun ring du 'tsho ba zhes pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:1259: der 'dzin gyi skyes bu dam pa 'gro ba'i phan
NK039(ti)004:1260: bde spel bar bzhed pa rnams kyi zhabs pad brten
NK039(ti)004:1261: cing bzhed don gegs med par 'grub par mdzad du
NK039(ti)004:1262: gsol / bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa'i dpal dang grags pa spel /
NK039(ti)004:1264: skye bo sdang bar byed pa'i dgra sod /
NK039(ti)004:1265: 'byung po gnod par byed pa'i bgegs thul /
NK039(ti)004:1266: lha 'dres bar du gcod pa'i rkyen bzlog /
NK039(ti)004:1267: dus ma yin pa'i 'chi bdag gi bdud bsgyur /
NK039(ti)004:1268: gnod byed bar du gcod pa thams cad thal ba rdul phran bzhin du brlag par mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)004:1270: b+h+yoh 'phrul gyi pho brang thod pa'i lding khang nas //
NK039(ti)004:1271: dpal ldan lha mo khrag 'thung re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1272: srin po nag po'i chung ma ral pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1273: ya mtshan rmad byung lha mo khro rgyal gtso //
NK039(ti)004:1274: zhal gdongs mche gtsigs drag po'i rkan sgra can //
NK039(ti)004:1275: rngam pa'i tshul gyi dmar chen khrag la rol //
NK039(ti)004:1276: kha 'bar chen mo srog gi shan pa mo //
NK039(ti)004:1277: sku ni nag mo 'bum gyi dbus na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:1278: skye ba rnam bzhi sgrol ba'i ging chen mo //
NK039(ti)004:1279: khyod ni srid pa gsum gyis bskul bar 'os //
NK039(ti)004:1280: tshangs pa'i rgyal pos rma bya'i rgyal mtshan phul //
NK039(ti)004:1281: bdud kyi rgyal pos khram bam nag po 'phul //
NK039(ti)004:1282: 'chi bdag rgyal pos phyag mtshan ral gri dur khrod
NK039(ti)004:1283: ma mos b+hany+dza lcang lo gnod sbyin rgyal pos nee'u'i
NK039(ti)004:1284: rkyal pa phul / klu yi rgyal pos sbrul nag
NK039(ti)004:1285: gdengs ka khyab 'jug chen pos nyi ma zla ba
NK039(ti)004:1286: rnam thos sras kyi seng ge snyan cha theg chen
NK039(ti)004:1287: rgyal pos glang chen ko rlon ma bdud rgyal mos
NK039(ti)004:1289: ma mo rnams kyis nad kyis rkyal pa klu mo
NK039(ti)004:1290: rnams kyi 'phrul gyi me long sman mo rnams kyi
NK039(ti)004:1291: mtshon gyi gru gu sha za'i rgyal pos thod pa'i
NK039(ti)004:1292: phreng ba lha phran rnams kyi gser gyi dril bu
NK039(ti)004:1293: sa bdag rgyal pos rus sbal phog gu btsan gyi
NK039(ti)004:1294: rgyal pos shwa d+hel dkar nag srin po'i rgyal pos
NK039(ti)004:1295: lcags sgrog 'bar ba rnal 'byor bdag gis bdud rtsi'i
NK039(ti)004:1296: gtor ma 'phul // rak+ta dmar gyi ar+g+ham bsgrengs tsam na //
NK039(ti)004:1297: ma la bus 'bod gdung sems ma chung bar /
NK039(ti)004:1298: smug nag 'jigs pa'i rgyal mo'i skur bzhengs la //
NK039(ti)004:1299: lcags kyu 'dra ba'i sder mos gtor ma longs //
NK039(ti)004:1300: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i zhal gdong la //
NK039(ti)004:1301: za byed rno gdug 'bar ba'i mche bas gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1302: le brgan khra 'thung 'bar ba'i ljags rkyang la //
NK039(ti)004:1303: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa'i mgul du bstims //
NK039(ti)004:1305: b+h+yoh lha la dbang bsgyur lha mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)004:1306: dbang phyug sras mo dkar mo dung skyong ma //
NK039(ti)004:1307: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)004:1308: lha mo dpal 'bar ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1309: klu la dbang bsgyur klu mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)004:1310: gtsug na rin chen bu mo yid 'ong ma //
NK039(ti)004:1311: rol pa'i mtsho bdun gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)004:1312: klu mo dpal 'bar ma la gnod sbyin dbang bsgyur gnod sbyin dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)004:1313: gang ba bzang bo'i bu mo shang kar ti //
NK039(ti)004:1314: nags tshal d+r+wa ba can gyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)004:1315: gnod sbyin re ma ti bdud la dbang bsgyur bdud mo dpa' 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)004:1316: re lde mgo nyag bu mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1317: bdud mkhar rtse dgu'i gnas kyi gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)004:1318: bdud mo re ma ti sangs rgyas bstan pa srung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK039(ti)004:1319: chos nyid don rtogs 'phags ma re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1320: sa brgyad non pa'i sems ma re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1321: lha mo mthu chen khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1322: dkon mchog mthu chen khyed la rnal 'byor dgra 'dul khyed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1324: b+h+yoh ma bcos chos sku bde ba chen po las //
NK039(ti)004:1325: srid dang zhi bar mi gnas mnyam pa nyid //
NK039(ti)004:1326: yon tan phrin las mtshon pa'i skur ston pa //
NK039(ti)004:1327: dpal dang ldan pa'i lha mo khyod la 'dud //
NK039(ti)004:1328: sku yi dkyil 'khor chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam //
NK039(ti)004:1329: mya ngan mi 'da' mthun par snang ba nyid //
NK039(ti)004:1330: mdzes pa'i rgyan ldan ma gcig re m+aa ti //
NK039(ti)004:1331: 'gro ba'i gnyan gcig ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1332: chos sku mkha' ltar rtogs pa'i shes rab la //
NK039(ti)004:1333: thugs rjes rmad du byung ba'i thabs tshul gyis //
NK039(ti)004:1334: ma rung gdug pa can rnams tshar gcod cing //
NK039(ti)004:1335: mi bsnyel thugs dam can la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)004:1336: dman pa mi 'dor rtags su bong bu bcibs //
NK039(ti)004:1337: lha'i lhar gyur lha min skrag mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1338: rdzu 'phrul shugs 'chang stong gsum khyab par nyul //
NK039(ti)004:1339: bstan pa gnyer mdzad ma la bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)004:1340: khyung po rnal 'byor gyis mdzad pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:1341: b+h+yoh dpal gyi srung ma khams gsum gtso mo ni /
NK039(ti)004:1342: bong bu rta mchog dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)004:1343: nag mo khrag 'thung dbyings kyi da pal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)004:1344: dpal ldan ma chen cir yang 'khrul pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1345: stong khams kun la dbang mdzad chen mo bzhi //
NK039(ti)004:1346: nam zla dpyid kyi rgyal mor gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)004:1347: dkar mo sh+ri ri dur khrod gnas nyul ma //
NK039(ti)004:1348: khrag 'thung chen mo'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1349: 'gro ba kun la bde ba stsol ba'i slad //
NK039(ti)004:1350: nam zla dbyar gyi rgyal mos gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)004:1351: b+ha ga histi mkha' las char 'bebs ma //
NK039(ti)004:1352: ser mo sbyor bdag chen mor phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1353: khams gsum kun tu bskyod cing bsdud pa'i slad //
NK039(ti)004:1354: nam zla ston gyi rgyal mor gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)004:1355: sprul pa mthing nag mi srun ral pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1356: ma mo srog bdag chen mor log 'dren dgra bgegs thal bar brlag pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1357: nam zla dgun gyi rgyal mor gshegs me zla brag gyon rgya mtsho'i gting nyul ma //
NK039(ti)004:1358: khri za stong sgrol chen mor b+h+yoh dam ldan rnams la rtag 'du phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1359: rgya mtsho'i klong nas me mched cing //
NK039(ti)004:1361: mun pa'i dkyil na me 'bar nas //
NK039(ti)004:1362: re ti dpon g.yog mkha' la 'gro //
NK039(ti)004:1363: mtshan mo 'jigs rung sbeg pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)004:1364: keng rus gar rtse'i dur khrod rol //
NK039(ti)004:1365: dur bya lding ba rnams bskor ba'i //
NK039(ti)004:1366: dur khrod rnams na las brtson cing //
NK039(ti)004:1367: dgu dang bcu gcig nyer bzhi'i tshes //
NK039(ti)004:1368: gsang sngags bsgrub dang sde snod kyi //
NK039(ti)004:1369: dam chos 'dzin skyongs rgyud la bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1370: de dag dus bzhi'i bstod pa'o //
NK039(ti)004:1371: b+h+yoh gru gsum mthing nag zhal gyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)004:1372: dur khrod mnga' mdzad dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1373: 'das dang ma byon kun la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK039(ti)004:1374: stong gsum 'jig rten kun gyi mdangs 'phrog ma //
NK039(ti)004:1375: kun la dbang bsgyur 'khor lo rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1376: bsam pa'i don grub nor bu rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1377: mi 'bral gzugs mdzes btsun mo rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1378: bla med grogs tshol blon po rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1379: theg pa'i mchog ldan glang po rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1380: sa bcu bgrod mdzad rta mchog rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1381: 'jig rten mgon skyabs dmag dpon rin chen 'dra //
NK039(ti)004:1382: mah 'jig rten mgon po ltar ni bsod nams che //
NK039(ti)004:1383: lha dbang brgya byin ltar na longs spyod che //
NK039(ti)004:1384: u ma de wa ltar ni cho rigs btsun //
NK039(ti)004:1385: u dum+wa ra ltar ni skye ba dkon //
NK039(ti)004:1386: me tog pad+ma ltar ni blta bas mdzes //
NK039(ti)004:1387: phyag na rdo rje ltar ni mthu stobs che //
NK039(ti)004:1388: gcan gzan seng ge ltar na dpa' brjid che //
NK039(ti)004:1389: nam mkha'i lha phran ltar ni sku khrus gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1390: nor bu rin chen ltar ni gtsug tu khur //
NK039(ti)004:1391: 'dzam gling rgyal po ltar ni bdag bstod do //
NK039(ti)004:1392: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la /
NK039(ti)004:1393: bskangs gsol bskul pa gtor 'bul gsum /
NK039(ti)004:1394: mtha' bsdus bkra shis rim pa dang lnga /
NK039(ti)004:1395: dang po la bskang gsol dngos dang /
NK039(ti)004:1401: h'u big+nana ta krita h'u phatah ram yam kham s+w+aa b+h+aa wa rnams kyis sbyangs /
NK039(ti)004:1402: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum yig las byung ba 'jigs rung thod pa bso lcags kyi mkhar /
NK039(ti)004:1404: mi ro'i rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba'i nang du dam nyams
NK039(ti)004:1405: dgra bo bsgral ba'i mgo rus don snod dbang lnga
NK039(ti)004:1411: mi nag dbang po tshangs shing rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)004:1412: stag gzigs gos dar sogs phyi nang gsang ba'i dam
NK039(ti)004:1413: rdzas dngos 'byor yid sprul gyi bskangs rdzas zag med
NK039(ti)004:1414: nam mkha'i mdzod du 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:1415: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas spel /
NK039(ti)004:1416: rgyas par spro na 'khrugs bskangs chen mo sbyar zhing /
NK039(ti)004:1417: dkyus tsam du snyan pa'i dbyangs rol bcas /
NK039(ti)004:1418: b+h+yoh yongs 'dus shing gi gnas mchog nas //
NK039(ti)004:1419: rin chen mdzes pa'i pho brang nas //
NK039(ti)004:1420: bde ldan 'phrul gyis lding khang nang //
NK039(ti)004:1421: 'gying bag tshul gyis gar mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1422: dbang phyug sras mo dung skyongs ma //
NK039(ti)004:1423: gdung bas spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1424: chibs su bong bu dmar gwa bcibs //
NK039(ti)004:1425: ral gri nee'u le phyag na bsnams //
NK039(ti)004:1426: sku la dur khrod chas kyi brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1427: dpal ldan lha mo gnas 'dir byon //
NK039(ti)004:1428: byang shar thod pa'i sku mkhar na //
NK039(ti)004:1429: mi ro 'bum gyi khri steng nas //
NK039(ti)004:1430: drel nag rkang gsum chibs su bcibs //
NK039(ti)004:1431: sku mdog nag mo re ldes brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1432: phyag na khram bam shwa d+hil bsnams //
NK039(ti)004:1433: bdud mo chen mo gnas 'dir gshegs //
NK039(ti)004:1434: klu rnams dbang bsdud chu srin gdong //
NK039(ti)004:1435: bka'i blon po ba lam ma //
NK039(ti)004:1436: las kyi pho nya khri smon ma //
NK039(ti)004:1438: ma ma re ma ti sa p+aa ri wa ra
NK039(ti)004:1439: badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah h'u b+h+yoh dpal ldan
NK039(ti)004:1441: khyed kyi thugs dam bskang ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1442: sha khrag sna tshogs gtor ma la //
NK039(ti)004:1443: snying sna sna tshogs rgyal mtshan btsugs //
NK039(ti)004:1444: dar zab mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1445: sha chang sgog gtsong la sogs pa'i //
NK039(ti)004:1446: mchod rdzas sna tshogs gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)004:1447: tshil chen dud pa sprin ltar 'khrigs //
NK039(ti)004:1449: zhun chen mar me ta la la //
NK039(ti)004:1450: thod rnga mi rkang dung la sogs //
NK039(ti)004:1451: rol mo sna tshogs ti ri ri //
NK039(ti)004:1452: snyan pa'i dzab bgrang ye re re //
NK039(ti)004:1453: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)004:1454: mah bdag gis dus gsum dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)004:1455: dpal ldan lha mo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK039(ti)004:1456: sku gsung thugs dang 'gal ba rnams //
NK039(ti)004:1457: mchod sbyin 'di yis bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:1458: 'bod pa'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1459: zhing gi lpags pa'i g.yab mo dang //
NK039(ti)004:1460: g.yab dar nag pos thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)004:1461: brten pa'i dam rdzas tsit+ta snying gi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)004:1462: rang bzhin gnas nas spyan 'dren phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1463: tshil chen gsur gyi dud pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1464: mi rkang gling bus dam tshig gnyen po bsre ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1465: bdud rtsi sman gyis mgrin pa'i gsang nas sbyangs pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1466: dmar chen rak+tasa ljags kyi dbang po tshim bya'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1467: sha chen rus pas nyams chag ma lus gso ba'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1468: lha lug nag po spyi dkar dang //
NK039(ti)004:1469: bya nag sgo nga dkar mo la //
NK039(ti)004:1470: yon tan sna tshogs ldan pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1471: ma mo yongs kyi rma bya 'jol sgeg ldan pa la //
NK039(ti)004:1472: rin chen sna tshogs gshog pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1473: rin chen 'bar bas spyi bor brgyan //
