NK039(ti)004:1474: ma cig gtso mo'i de mo nag mo gser mig ma //
NK039(ti)004:1475: yid bzhin nor bus sku la brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1476: yon tan du mar ldan pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1477: khol lo re m+aa ti yi nal phrug snying dang sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)004:1478: seng ge snying dang bya nag snying //
NK039(ti)004:1479: nal spags seng ge'i rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK039(ti)004:1481: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskangs //
NK039(ti)004:1482: phyag na rdo rje'i thugs dam bskangs //
NK039(ti)004:1483: ma h+aa de wa'i u ma de wa'i dpal ldan
NK039(ti)004:1484: lha mo'i ma h+aa k+aa li'i bram ze mchog sred
NK039(ti)004:1486: bskang ngo bskal pa'i gshin rje'i chos rgyal re lde
NK039(ti)004:1487: mgo nyag dran pa dbang byed bdud mo re ti'i
NK039(ti)004:1488: bka' bzhin las rnams bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1489: chu srin gdong gis dgra bgegs rtsad nas gcod pa'i
NK039(ti)004:1490: ba lam nag mo'i bstan srungs pho nya 'byed pa'i
NK039(ti)004:1491: phyir // khri sman sa le'i rdo rje kun grags
NK039(ti)004:1492: rdo rje kun bzang rdo rje kun gsal rdo rje
NK039(ti)004:1493: ye shes rdo rje 'od chags rdo rje gsal 'phro
NK039(ti)004:1494: rdo rje g.yu sgron re ma dza yi re ma
NK039(ti)004:1495: dzu yi dkar mo mdzes ma sngon mo ral 'dzing
NK039(ti)004:1496: dmar mo dbang chen ser mo mkha' bzhad seng stag
NK039(ti)004:1497: 'brug spyang zhi ba'i las rnams bsgrub slad du //
NK039(ti)004:1498: shar gyi ma drug rgyas pa'i las rnams lho yi
NK039(ti)004:1499: ma drug dbang gi las rnams nub kyi ma drug
NK039(ti)004:1500: drag po'i las rnams byang gi ma drug tshad med
NK039(ti)004:1502: sgo ma bzhi yi smra bo lag ring la sogs pa //
NK039(ti)004:1503: smra bsrung brgyad dgra bgegs khram la 'debs pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1504: khram thogs brgyad stong gsum ma lus nyul ba'i bong zhon brgyad bya ba'i las rnams bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1505: nam gru brgyad 'khor du las kun bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1506: srid pa'i ma mo stong h'u /
NK039(ti)004:1507: sha za khrag 'thung las kyi srin mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)004:1508: stong phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi'i shar phyogs dkar mo
NK039(ti)004:1509: 'bum gyi lho phyogs ser mo 'bum gyi nub phyogs
NK039(ti)004:1510: dmar mo 'bum byang phyogs ljang mo mtha' bskor smug
NK039(ti)004:1511: mo 'bum sde'i sprul pa'i mthing nag 'bum sde'i ma
NK039(ti)004:1512: mo ma yams rgyal mo'i ma mo bye ba'i tshogs
NK039(ti)004:1513: kyi bdud mo bye ba'i tshogs dzam gling skyongs ma
NK039(ti)004:1515: bod khams brten ma bcu gnyis snang srid lha srin sde brgyad thugs dam bskangs //
NK039(ti)004:1517: b+h+yoh bde stong klong yang gang shar rol pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1518: cir yang 'char ba'i 'gags med ting 'dzin rtsal //
NK039(ti)004:1519: sna tshogs sgyu ma'i bkod pa kha phyes te //
NK039(ti)004:1520: ma khyed thugs dam bskang ba'i dpyid du spro //
NK039(ti)004:1521: gsar rnying thod brtsegs klad zhag zhal bas mdzes //
NK039(ti)004:1522: lcang lo'i kha bad rgyu mi'i d+r+wa phyed 'phyang //
NK039(ti)004:1523: dbugs bral rgyal mtshan zhing gi bla bre dkrigs //
NK039(ti)004:1524: rngams brjid rol pa drag po'i pho brang 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1525: 'dod khams dbang mo 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)004:1526: lcang lor bcas pa'i b+han+dza'i snod yong por //
NK039(ti)004:1527: nang gsang phyi yi dgra bgegs bsgral ba yi //
NK039(ti)004:1528: sha ri khrag mtsho rus pa'i gram khrod 'khrugs //
NK039(ti)004:1529: dgung snyed brag gi ri khro sa pa'i gtor ma 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1530: 'dod khams dbang mo brtan g.yo'i bcud len brgyad stong ra sa yan //
NK039(ti)004:1531: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho lbu ba'i phreng ba 'phar //
NK039(ti)004:1532: bdud rtsi'i skyems dang dbang lnga'i me tog gis //
NK039(ti)004:1533: 'dod khams dbang mo gzugs reg sgra snyan gsung zhim ro mchog bda' //
NK039(ti)004:1534: yid byung smin legs bu mo yid 'phrog mas //
NK039(ti)004:1535: legs par mchod pa'i ngo mtshar bkod pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1536: rnam mang mig 'phrul lta bur rtse ba yis //
NK039(ti)004:1537: 'dod khams dbang mo 'dzam gling yud kyis bskor ba'i cang shes dang //
NK039(ti)004:1538: mi sdug rwa can 'gying ba'i g.yag zhol chen //
NK039(ti)004:1539: spu sdug 'jom legs g.yang mo mig sman mdog /
NK039(ti)004:1540: rdo rje'i mchu sder dgra bgegs klad 'gem byas //
NK039(ti)004:1541: 'dod khams dbang mo rnam bkra'i mdangs gsal rma bya'i rgyal mtshan dang //
NK039(ti)004:1542: lhab lhub g.yo ba'i dar gyi 'phan bzang po //
NK039(ti)004:1543: dbang po'i gzhu 'dra ba dan lda ldib dang /
NK039(ti)004:1544: mi dbang las skyes rten gyi phreng ba 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1545: 'dod khams dbang mo phyi nang gsang mchod bkra shis rtags rdzas dang //
NK039(ti)004:1546: sna bdun rin chen ngo mtshar nor bu'i ri //
NK039(ti)004:1547: sra zhing brtan pa rdo rje'i go dang khrab //
NK039(ti)004:1548: phas rgol dgra 'joms mtshon cha'i 'khrul 'khor sogs //
NK039(ti)004:1549: 'dod khams dbang mo 'jigs rung mi nag gnas du 'o dod 'bod //
NK039(ti)004:1550: sha za mche gtsigs srin mo skan sgra gtogs //
NK039(ti)004:1551: mon mo dug 'debs ci spyang ngur skad ldir //
NK039(ti)004:1552: dar gyi cod pan g.yo ba'i khyi nag gis //
NK039(ti)004:1553: 'dod khams dbang mo 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)004:1554: lang ka'i yul gyi mgrin bzang dmar gwa la //
NK039(ti)004:1555: srin thod sga dang lpags pas rab g.yogs shing //
NK039(ti)004:1556: gong smed srab mthur gdug pa'i sbrul gyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1557: dzam gling yud kyis bskor ba'i bzhon pa 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1558: 'dod khams dbang mo mi lpags gos dang re lde'i smad g.yogs dang //
NK039(ti)004:1559: rma bya'i gdug dang nyi ma zla ba'i brgyan //
NK039(ti)004:1560: 'tshubs rlung gur khang khrag nag zhag gi rdzing //
NK039(ti)004:1561: sra rno khro chu'i ral gri sdig pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1562: 'dod khams dbang mo 'khor bcas bdud khrag thod bkang ne'u le'i rkyal pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1563: nad kyi dpal bu tshon gyi gru gu dang //
NK039(ti)004:1564: bdud kyi khram shing shwa d+hil dkar nag dang //
NK039(ti)004:1565: mda' dar me long dung shwas brgyan pa sogs //
NK039(ti)004:1566: 'dod khams dbang mo mgo rlon khrag 'dzag g.yo ba'i do shal dang //
NK039(ti)004:1567: rak+ta'i byugs pa thal chen tshom bu dang //
NK039(ti)004:1568: glang chen ko ba dug sbrul gdu bu dang //
NK039(ti)004:1569: phyag rgya lnga dang snyan rgyan seng ge sbrul //
NK039(ti)004:1570: 'dod khams dbang mo bkod legs gser ri rol mtshos 'khyud pa'i ri //
NK039(ti)004:1571: gling bzhi gling phran nyi zla dpag bsam shing //
NK039(ti)004:1572: rin chen gter bum dgos 'dod 'byung ba dang //
NK039(ti)004:1573: lha mi longs spyod dpal 'byor legs sprul pas //
NK039(ti)004:1574: 'dod khams dbang mo chos dbyings bzang mo e ka dza ti ma //
NK039(ti)004:1575: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'dod khams dbang phyug gi //
NK039(ti)004:1576: skur bzhengs ye shes ma mo lhun gyis grub //
NK039(ti)004:1577: yid ches gsol 'debs bla med rten mchog 'dis //
NK039(ti)004:1578: 'dod khams dbang mo de ltar dgyes mchod bskangs shing bshags pa'i mthus //
NK039(ti)004:1579: ma yi mthu stobs nyi ma bye ba'i gzis //
NK039(ti)004:1580: bdud sde'i ku mud zum pas bstan 'dzin gyi //
NK039(ti)004:1581: 'dabs stong nyams med phyogs brgyar dar bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1584: rdo rje rgyal po bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' //
NK039(ti)004:1585: gsang sngags rnal 'byor mnyes pa'i grub pa mo //
NK039(ti)004:1586: yon tan mang pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1587: sngon gyi las kyi 'brel bas bdag bzung ste //
NK039(ti)004:1588: sku gsum sgyu mar bstan pa'i bka' drin can //
NK039(ti)004:1589: dus ngan snyigs ma'i dus 'dir bdag skyes te //
NK039(ti)004:1590: ma rig nyon mongs bdag med dbang gyur te //
NK039(ti)004:1591: dam tshig nyams shing thugs dang 'gal gyur pa //
NK039(ti)004:1592: rdo rje dam ldan ma la bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1593: rgyas par spro na 'khrugs bskang gi mjug nas sbyar /
NK039(ti)004:1594: b+h+yoh thod pa dgu brtsegs srid pa'i gzhal yas nas //
NK039(ti)004:1595: dpal ldan lha mo gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1596: rang la rig pa'i ye shes rgyud ldan yang //
NK039(ti)004:1597: 'phral byung log rtog shin tu dbang che bas //
NK039(ti)004:1598: ma yi thugs dang 'gal ba bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1599: gshin rje ye nas lha mo'i khyo yin yang //
NK039(ti)004:1600: phrag dog dbang gis bgyis pa rlung nag ye nas lha mo'i sprul yin kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1601: log par bltas te ma dad bong bu ye nas lha mo'i bcibs yin kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1602: ma brten brdeg par gyur nal ma ye nas lha mo'i grogs yin yang //
NK039(ti)004:1603: log par bltas te gshe ba nal bu ye nas lha mo'i sras yin kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1604: ma brten bskrad par gyur pa yug sa ye nas lha mo'i dgra yin kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1605: 'dod chags dbang gis spyod pa phag rdzi ye nas lha mo'i khyo yin kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1606: ma brten bskrad par gyur pa mgar ba ye nas lha mo'i dgra yin kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1607: ma bskrad brten par slob dpon thugs 'gal dam nyams 'dres pa sogs //
NK039(ti)004:1608: bdag cag ma rig gyur pa bdag cag ye nas ser sna'i dbang gyur pas //
NK039(ti)004:1609: mchod tshogs gtor ma zhan pa le lo snyoms las dbang du gyur lags pas //
NK039(ti)004:1610: mchod pa lo zlar 'das pa bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1611: gtor ma dus las yol la gcom la 'phyar bas man ngag gsang ma thub //
NK039(ti)004:1612: zab mo'i thugs dang 'gal ba bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1613: mah khyed kyi thugs dam bskangs nas kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1614: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa yi //
NK039(ti)004:1615: lus ngag yid gsum bya ba rnams //
NK039(ti)004:1616: nyams par gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK039(ti)004:1617: dam can khyed la mthol lo bshags //
NK039(ti)004:1618: phyin chad nyes pa mi bgyi 'tshal //
NK039(ti)004:1619: bskang ngo bshags so bzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1620: yi ge brgya pa lan bdun bzla /
NK039(ti)004:1623: b+h+yoh ma g.yel ma g.yel ma cig ma //
NK039(ti)004:1624: ma g.yel ma g.yel bdud mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)004:1625: ma g.yel de ni pha bi nas //
NK039(ti)004:1626: sprin nag 'khrugs pa'i klong rol nas //
NK039(ti)004:1627: srin gyi rgyal mo skur bzhengs nas //
NK039(ti)004:1628: bskul ba'i gnas 'dir byon tu gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1629: mah ma cig lha mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK039(ti)004:1630: rdo rje lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1631: nad dang rim gyi mnga' bdag ma //
NK039(ti)004:1632: sad dang ser ba'i sna 'dren ma //
NK039(ti)004:1633: dam nyams kun gyi srog gcod ma //
NK039(ti)004:1634: dam tshig can gyi grogs mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1635: rnal 'byor yongs kyi dgra lha mo //
NK039(ti)004:1636: skye 'gro'i srog la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1637: 'byung po yongs kyi rje mo khyod //
NK039(ti)004:1638: dgra bo'i dus mtha' bstung byed ma //
NK039(ti)004:1639: khams gsum za ba'i za mkhan ma //
NK039(ti)004:1640: srid gsum za ba'i mthu mo che //
NK039(ti)004:1641: mah mthing nag gcer bu ral pa can //
NK039(ti)004:1643: shangs nas nad kyi rlangs pa 'thul //
NK039(ti)004:1644: chibs su dril sngon rlung gshogs bcibs //
NK039(ti)004:1645: res 'ga' khros nas chal chol byed //
NK039(ti)004:1646: srid pa'i bong bu dmar ga zhon //
NK039(ti)004:1647: g.yas na gdug pa'i ral gri 'phyar //
NK039(ti)004:1648: srid gsum ma lus rtsad nas gcod //
NK039(ti)004:1649: g.yon na gdug pa'i thod khrag thog /
NK039(ti)004:1650: skye 'gro'i srog la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)004:1651: ma b+h+yoh ma g.yel ma g.yel dam la dgongs //
NK039(ti)004:1652: ma cig bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1653: phyag brnyan bdud mo 'bum sde rnams //
NK039(ti)004:1654: bu la sdang ba'i dgra byung gi //
NK039(ti)004:1655: ma cig lha mo ra mda' log /
NK039(ti)004:1656: sdang ba'i dgra la phrin las mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1657: ma cig thugs dam dus la bab //
NK039(ti)004:1658: bcol pa'i las la mthu ma chung //
NK039(ti)004:1659: dam tshig yal bar ma btang bar //
NK039(ti)004:1660: bu yi phrin las myur du bsgrubs //
NK039(ti)004:1661: ma cig bdud mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1662: khyod kyi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK039(ti)004:1663: las kyi pho nya bdud mo 'bum //
NK039(ti)004:1664: nag mo rngam pa'i nga ro can //
NK039(ti)004:1665: ma bdud nag mo 'khor dang bcas //
NK039(ti)004:1666: sngags pas bos shing bskul ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)004:1667: mig nas khrag gi mchi ma 'dzag /
NK039(ti)004:1668: kha nas gdug pa'i ngan sngags sgrogs //
NK039(ti)004:1669: zhal nas kus 'debs stong gsum gang //
NK039(ti)004:1670: nad kyi kha phru dgra la 'debs //
NK039(ti)004:1671: mtshan zhing dpag tshad brgyad khrir rgyug /
NK039(ti)004:1672: bdud mo nag mo 'khor bcas rnams //
NK039(ti)004:1673: bdag gi las su khyod mchod na //
NK039(ti)004:1674: bdag la sdong ba'i dgra bo 'di //
NK039(ti)004:1675: lo dang zla bar ma btang bar //
NK039(ti)004:1676: zhag dang za mar dus mtha' bstungs //
NK039(ti)004:1677: srog rtsa dmar po rgal nas chod //
NK039(ti)004:1678: snying khrag dron mo kha nas drongs //
NK039(ti)004:1679: kun bzhi'i rnam shes gzhi nas shigs //
NK039(ti)004:1680: gzugs phung thal ba rdul du rlog /
NK039(ti)004:1681: ma la bcol nas phrin las mdzad //
NK039(ti)004:1682: bu la sdang ba'i dgra byung gi //
NK039(ti)004:1683: ma cig bu la mi dgongs sam //
NK039(ti)004:1684: ming la sdang ba'i dgra byung gis //
NK039(ti)004:1685: sring gcig phrin las mi mdzad dam //
NK039(ti)004:1686: bdag la sdang ba'i dgra byung gi //
NK039(ti)004:1687: bran gcig rje la mi dgongs sam //
NK039(ti)004:1688: mah ma mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)004:1689: khyod kyi las kyi pho nya ni //
NK039(ti)004:1692: gos su mi lpags rlon pa gyon //
NK039(ti)004:1693: zas su mi sha rta sha za //
NK039(ti)004:1694: skom du mi khrag rta khrag 'thung //
NK039(ti)004:1695: las su sangs rgyas bstan pa srungs //
NK039(ti)004:1696: srog gcod las la shin tu dgyes //
NK039(ti)004:1697: phyag g.yas ral gri 'bar ba yis //
NK039(ti)004:1698: bstan la sdang byed srog rtsa gcod //
NK039(ti)004:1699: phyag g.yas gdug pa'i thod khrag thogs //
NK039(ti)004:1700: dgra bo'i sems kyi mar me sod //
NK039(ti)004:1701: ma bdud nag mo'i 'khor tshogs rnams //
NK039(ti)004:1702: sngon gyi dam tshig ma g.yel bar //
NK039(ti)004:1703: sha khrag dmar gtor 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)004:1704: khyed la bcol pa'i phrin las ni //
NK039(ti)004:1705: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig byed dang //
NK039(ti)004:1706: rdo rje slob dpon smod byed dang //
NK039(ti)004:1707: bstan la sdang byed dgra bo 'di //
NK039(ti)004:1708: ma bdud nag mo'i 'khor tshogs kyi //
NK039(ti)004:1709: rengs par khug la gzugs la phob //
NK039(ti)004:1710: 'du ba rnam bzhi nas sogs khongs nas slong //
NK039(ti)004:1711: dran pa med par smyo 'bog brgyal du chug /
NK039(ti)004:1712: gzhung pa dkar po'i srog rtsa brgal nas chod //
NK039(ti)004:1713: mkhal ma g.yu rgong gsang ba'i gnas nas drongs //
NK039(ti)004:1714: srog rtsa dmar po lus kyi rgyab nas chod //
NK039(ti)004:1715: kha nas lag chug khong pa'i snying nas drongs //
NK039(ti)004:1716: dran pa rnam shes tsit+ta'i dkyil nas drongs //
NK039(ti)004:1717: lhan cig skyes pa'i lha dang phyes //
NK039(ti)004:1718: mnyam por 'ong ba'i bdud dang sprod //
NK039(ti)004:1719: 'go ba'i lha lnga'i lag nas khug /
NK039(ti)004:1720: sngags dang rdzas kyi nus pa 'phrog /
NK039(ti)004:1721: sa la brten pa'i brten phur phud //
NK039(ti)004:1723: gri thabs nyi shu rtsa lngas sod //
NK039(ti)004:1724: bdun rgyud tshun chad rtsad nas chod //
NK039(ti)004:1725: gtan nas brlag pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK039(ti)004:1726: ma cig thugs dam dus la bab //
NK039(ti)004:1727: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1729: sngon ri bo ma la ya yi rtse mor dpal
NK039(ti)004:1730: phyag na rdo rjer khyed kyi srog gi snying po
NK039(ti)004:1731: phul ba bzhin / rtsa ba dang rgyud par bcas
NK039(ti)004:1732: pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi dam las ma
NK039(ti)004:1733: phul ba bzhin / 'da' bar / bstan pa la
NK039(ti)004:1734: sdang ba'i dgra bo 'di lo dang zla bar ma
NK039(ti)004:1735: phul ba bzhin / 'da' bar / bzhag / zhag dang za mar ma 'gor /
NK039(ti)004:1736: tshe phyi ma la dus ma 'debs /
NK039(ti)004:1737: nam mkha' stong pa la tshad ma btsugs /
NK039(ti)004:1738: las kyi rnam par smin pa la khung ma byed
NK039(ti)004:1739: bar da lta nyid du dus kyi mtha' bstung zhig
NK039(ti)004:1741: gzugs kyi phung po shig cig /
NK039(ti)004:1742: srog gi rtsa ba cod cig /
NK039(ti)004:1743: sems kyi mar me sod cig /
NK039(ti)004:1744: lus sems kha sbyor phyes shig /
NK039(ti)004:1746: tshe bsod dbang thang snub cig /
NK039(ti)004:1747: bkrag mdong longs spyod phrog cig /
NK039(ti)004:1751: thal ba rdul du brlag par mdzad du gsol /
NK039(ti)004:1752: rgyud nas 'byung ba'i dpon g.yog gnad bskul basngagasa /
NK039(ti)004:1753: ru ru tsa h'uh a shug me ba dri ru
NK039(ti)004:1754: tra kha sha la nag mo h'u rak+sha tsit+ta ma
NK039(ti)004:1755: h+aa sa ma ti ma ru kha tsit+ta nan /
NK039(ti)004:1756: rak+mo ti ki ma dzah ma ma ti ti h'u
NK039(ti)004:1757: b+h+yoh ma ma sa ma ya re ma ti las
NK039(ti)004:1759: bsgrub pa dang 'brel na smad las drag po'i rim
NK039(ti)004:1760: pa mkhyen dbang nas bsgrul bstabs kyi bar du bya
NK039(ti)004:1766: gtor ma la zan ling khrag skyu 'bru sogs 'bul la /
NK039(ti)004:1768: rje btsun rtsa rgyud kyi dpal ldan bla ma dam
NK039(ti)004:1769: pa mchog gsum bla na med pa'i bka' bden pa
NK039(ti)004:1770: dang / mthu chen dam pa rdo rje'i chos skyong
NK039(ti)004:1771: ba'i srung ma'i dbang po bka' sdod drag shul rgya
NK039(ti)004:1772: mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyis bden bla med
NK039(ti)004:1773: ma mo rol pa khrag 'thung rbod gtong gi rgyal
NK039(ti)004:1774: mo ma 'khor dang bcas pa'i bden gsang sngags dang
NK039(ti)004:1775: rig sngags dang gzung sngags dang snying po phyag rgya
NK039(ti)004:1777: chos nyid rnam par dag cing chos can bslu ba
NK039(ti)004:1778: med pa'i bden pa bden pa chen po'i mthu la
NK039(ti)004:1779: bsten nas / bstan pa la sdang ba'i dgra dang /
NK039(ti)004:1780: bstan 'dzin la sdang ba'i dgrar gyur pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:1781: gnod par byed pa'i nyams pa'i bgegs kyi tshogs srid
NK039(ti)004:1782: pa gsum gyi khams gang na gnas kyang skad cig
NK039(ti)004:1783: yud tsam la 'dir mchis par gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:1786: n+ri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah tram yam dzah tri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah dzahmh'u bam ho /
NK039(ti)004:1787: zhes bkug pa'i gtor ma la spos sam dpal 'bar btsugs te /
NK039(ti)004:1788: ma h+aa k+aa li a be sha ya /
NK039(ti)004:1789: a ti ma ti sa ma tish+than+tu /
NK039(ti)004:1790: ma ma de wi ma h+aa k+aa li re ma
NK039(ti)004:1791: ti b+ha ling ta kha kha kh+aa hi ma h+aa
NK039(ti)004:1792: p+au tsa ho / a mri ta kha hi /
NK039(ti)004:1793: gsum bdun nam nyer gcig gis phul la /
NK039(ti)004:1795: b+h+yoh rdo rje gdan gyi shing drung nas //
NK039(ti)004:1796: phyogs phyogs de ni pha be nas //
NK039(ti)004:1797: nyi ma byang shar pha ki na //
NK039(ti)004:1798: lhun po chu gter gser ri can //
NK039(ti)004:1799: yongs 'dus shing gi rtsa ba na //
NK039(ti)004:1800: mtsho mu le mthing gi nang shed nas //
NK039(ti)004:1801: byang thang de ni bya ma byed //
NK039(ti)004:1802: byang ri de ni gya ma gyu //
NK039(ti)004:1803: byang rtse de ni bya ma byur //
NK039(ti)004:1804: byang lam de ni bra ma breng //
NK039(ti)004:1805: de 'dre'i thang gi ma zur na //
NK039(ti)004:1807: brag dang chu 'thabs ma zur na //
NK039(ti)004:1808: mtsho gcig de ni me re re //
NK039(ti)004:1809: mu le mtsho yi nang shed nas //
NK039(ti)004:1810: mthing gur smug po ldi ri ri //
NK039(ti)004:1811: mthing gur smug po ldir tsam na //
NK039(ti)004:1812: gser gyi tshugs shing rengs se reng //
NK039(ti)004:1813: dngul gyi chon thag brengs se breng //
NK039(ti)004:1814: dung gi chon phur khra la la //
NK039(ti)004:1815: de 'dra'i gur gyi nang shed na //
NK039(ti)004:1816: mi ro 'bum ni khri ru brtsigs //
NK039(ti)004:1817: rta ro 'bum ni gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)004:1818: mi khrag rta khrag 'dam rdzab g.yo //
NK039(ti)004:1819: zhing chen bsnol ba'i khri steng na //
NK039(ti)004:1820: ma cig lha mo bzhugs pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1821: lha mo yongs kyi klong dkyil na //
NK039(ti)004:1822: gcer bu 'dug pas gzi mdangs can //
NK039(ti)004:1824: mah e ka dza ti de na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:1825: dpal ldan lha mo de na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:1826: bdud kyi yum gcig de na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:1827: gshin rje'i lcam gcig de na bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:1828: mah ru lu b+h+yo yi dzab+da bgrangs zhing //
NK039(ti)004:1831: ma cig lha mo sku bskyod 'tshal //
NK039(ti)004:1832: ma cig lha mo sku bskyod tsa //
NK039(ti)004:1833: chibs su dril rta rkang gsum dang //
NK039(ti)004:1834: res dga' srin gyi bong bu bcibs //
NK039(ti)004:1835: g.yu mthur sngon po brengs se breng //
NK039(ti)004:1836: gser khrab ser po si li li //
NK039(ti)004:1837: gser sga phug po wangs se wang //
NK039(ti)004:1838: za 'og dar stan lhubs se lhub //
NK039(ti)004:1839: dar sna'i glo lan chums se chum //
NK039(ti)004:1840: sbrul nag gong smed khyugs se khyug /
NK039(ti)004:1841: dngul dkar yob chen khra la la //
NK039(ti)004:1842: drel rta'i rna ba g.yas pa la //
NK039(ti)004:1843: dar nag cod pan pu ru ru //
NK039(ti)004:1844: drel rta'i rna ba g.yon pa la //
NK039(ti)004:1845: le brgan dar sna pu ru ru //
NK039(ti)004:1846: mah ma cig lha mo sku bskyod tshal //
NK039(ti)004:1847: drel skad lan gsum steng du 'tsher //
NK039(ti)004:1848: steng gi lha rnams dbang du bsdud //
NK039(ti)004:1849: drel mjug lan gsum bar du g.yug /
NK039(ti)004:1850: bar gyi btsan rnams dbang du drel rmig lan gsum sa la brdung //
NK039(ti)004:1851: 'og gi klu rnams dbang du bsdus //
NK039(ti)004:1852: b+h+yoh ma cig lha mo sku bskyod 'tshal //
NK039(ti)004:1853: ma cig lha mo bskyed tsam na //
NK039(ti)004:1854: ban ngan phur kha ma yis bzlog /
NK039(ti)004:1855: ban ngan zor kha ma lo keg zla keg bdud
NK039(ti)004:1856: kyi zhags pa gshin rje'i khram kha chags chen nyam
NK039(ti)004:1857: nga rlung mkhris bad kan 'du ba yi //
NK039(ti)004:1858: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1859: ma cig lha mos bzlog tu gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1860: mah 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK039(ti)004:1861: bcol pa'i phrin las 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1863: rnga gling rol mor bcas bsgrub khang gi steng du gtor ma 'degs te /
NK039(ti)004:1864: b+h+yoh kahthoga pa sogs rtsa rgyud bla ma'i gnas //
NK039(ti)004:1865: kha ba can 'dir theg mchog bstan pa'i gzhi //
NK039(ti)004:1866: gang gi bshad sgrub chos kyi dpal 'phel slad //
NK039(ti)004:1867: nga ror bcas te lha mo khyod la 'bod //
NK039(ti)004:1868: ca co chen mos bdud kyi rna ba dral //
NK039(ti)004:1869: cha lugs srin mo khros pa'i skur ston pa //
NK039(ti)004:1870: ja chang phud dang gtor ma 'di rol la //
NK039(ti)004:1871: nyams pa'i dgra bo chom la 'beb par mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1872: ta th+aa ga ta'i spyan sngar dam mnos ltar //
NK039(ti)004:1873: tha na nyin zhag gcig kyang ma g.yel bar //
NK039(ti)004:1874: da lta bdag gi mdun 'dir bzhugs pa bzhin //
NK039(ti)004:1875: nam yang chos byed bu la g.yel med srungs //
NK039(ti)004:1876: pa ra mi ta rgya mtsho'i rlabs bsdud cing //
NK039(ti)004:1877: pha mtha' bral ba'i smon lam mtha' med khyed //
NK039(ti)004:1878: ba su ta yi zhags pas nyams pa'i bgegs //
NK039(ti)004:1879: ma rung drag tu 'ching zhing za bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1880: tsa mun+di yum mig sman ltar gnag cing //
NK039(ti)004:1881: tshad med thugs kyi dgongs pa bstan pa'i dpal //
NK039(ti)004:1882: dzam gling kun tu khyab pa'i bka' 'khor bcas //
NK039(ti)004:1883: wa ler 'khrol ba'i rol gling 'dis bskul te //
NK039(ti)004:1884: zhwa yi tog ltar bkur nas rten 'di la //
NK039(ti)004:1885: zad med sprul pa'i bkod pa dang bcas bzhugs //
NK039(ti)004:1886: 'a cag bstan par dkar rnams rtag tu srungs //
NK039(ti)004:1887: ya bral lung rtogs 'dzin rnams za skal lags //
NK039(ti)004:1888: rab 'bar me ri'i lding khang 'tshubs lung bcas //
NK039(ti)004:1889: la lung med pa'i gtsug lag khang 'grim nas //
NK039(ti)004:1890: sha s+aa na spel rgyud sde'i bstan pa'i mgon //
NK039(ti)004:1891: sa chen gang ba'i sprul pa'i gtor ma bzhes //
NK039(ti)004:1892: ha ha rgyal rnga rtag tu brdung ba yis //
NK039(ti)004:1893: a ti rdzogs chen bstan pa'i bya ra mos //
NK039(ti)004:1894: hi hi'i bzhad sgra 'byin pa dang bcas te //
NK039(ti)004:1895: dam tshig gtor ma'i stegs 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1897: bram ze mchog sred kyis mdzad pa'i til mar ma'am /
NK039(ti)004:1899: ma no badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti ye //
NK039(ti)004:1900: gdong bzhi dbang po 'jug sred nye dbang drag po rnams kyang khyed basngagasa phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1901: 'chi med na chung tshogs kyis bskor ba legs bris dga' ba'i tshal du rtsen //
NK039(ti)004:1902: yongs 'dus rgyal po'i ljon pa'i rtsa bar mthung shun 'khrigs pa'i chu gter dbus //
NK039(ti)004:1903: dpal ldan rlung shugs dril bu'i sgra sgrog mi ro rengs za mkha' la 'gro //
NK039(ti)004:1904: rlung 'tshubs bu mo rlung gos klubs pa rlung gi phreng bar rol pa mo //
NK039(ti)004:1905: lho phyogs rgya mtshor chos rgyal gshin rje'i sring gcig 'gro kun srog bdag mo //
NK039(ti)004:1906: sa brgyad brnyes kyang bud med lus la bstan pa srung ba'i g.yar dam can //
NK039(ti)004:1907: basngagasa 'os kun gyis dpal 'dzin yid bzhin ya mtshan rmad byung 'phags ma ni //
NK039(ti)004:1908: k+aa li de wi wa ya we dang 'bar ma byin za 'thab pa'i dbus //
NK039(ti)004:1909: 'jigs rung 'jigs par ston kyang 'jigs pa sel mdzad bsam pa'i dom grub ma //
NK039(ti)004:1910: khyod sku mi sdug khro yang khyod thugs de ni 'gro la rtag tu byams //
NK039(ti)004:1911: bstan dgra rgyun du bsgral yang ngan song gnas nas de dag skyobs mdzad phyir //
NK039(ti)004:1912: srin po'i chung ma yin mod mkha' 'gro kun gyi gtso mor basngagasa pa'i yul //
NK039(ti)004:1913: 'jig rten tshul du ston kyang 'jig rten pa las mngon par 'phags pa ni //
NK039(ti)004:1914: sh+aakya seng ger sems bskyed rdo rje 'dzin pa'i khol mo mchog sred grogs //
NK039(ti)004:1915: rnal 'byor ma ste bstan dgra'i za byed 'khor ba rnams la 'dren pa mo //
NK039(ti)004:1916: bdud brdung byug pa bgegs 'joms ral gri dgra 'joms tho ba nyid kyang yin //
NK039(ti)004:1917: dur khrod rnams nyul nyin par thal chen sngo skya byugs pa'i kha dog can //
NK039(ti)004:1918: mtshan mo nag mo ga shal chu gnyer ltar 'khrugs 'o 'dzin kun tu g.yo //
NK039(ti)004:1919: smin ma'i me rtse dum dum chad pa'i tsha dbal mda' lnga pa la ster //
NK039(ti)004:1920: srin gyi klad phor khrag zhag zhos dkar 'thung ba 'di na rgyu ba de //
NK039(ti)004:1921: chu srin kems red mar bcas dam tshig dkyil 'khor stegs la gshegs nas kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1922: lcang lo'i zhags g.yo mi mgor sha lnga gtor ma'i rdzas la mgur ston khyod //
NK039(ti)004:1923: gang zhig 'di na srid gsum dbang mor thub pa'i bstan phyir bdag snying nas //
NK039(ti)004:1924: ang+ku shas bkug a la la hos ti ra pad+mara bzhugs gsol te //
NK039(ti)004:1925: dran pa la ni don rnams kun bsgrub brlabs chen rdo rje d+aak+ki ma //
NK039(ti)004:1926: kha kha kam kas sgras 'byin dur gling dag tu khyab par dur bdag mo //
NK039(ti)004:1927: srid pa'i mig bsgyur cir yang ston pa bde skyong ma h+aa mu dra la //
NK039(ti)004:1928: yid ni mngon par rol pas dad pa'i 'dod don gsol la bdag phyogs te //
NK039(ti)004:1929: bdag yid shing rta chos nor thar pa'i re ba nor bus phyur bur bkang //
NK039(ti)004:1930: dzam+bu gser gyi snye mas khyab 'dir bstan 'di phyogs las rnam rgyal ba //
NK039(ti)004:1931: ji srid dran pa de srid rtag tu dge legs bsam pa kun 'grub mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1932: 'di la ma chen dgyes pa'i mtshan ma yang pa dag yod do //
NK039(ti)004:1934: dam rdzas brgyan pa'i gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)004:1935: rnal 'byor bdag dang bdag gis 'khor rnams la //
NK039(ti)004:1936: bdud dang dgra bgegs thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK039(ti)004:1937: mi mthun gnod pa'i phyogs dang bral ba dang //
NK039(ti)004:1938: dpal dang 'byor pa tshe dang gzi mdangs dang //
NK039(ti)004:1939: 'khor dang longs spyod grags pa rgyas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)004:1940: bka' dang bstan pa bstan 'dzin kun srungs shig /
NK039(ti)004:1941: khyed la bdag gis 'dod pa gsol ba ni //
NK039(ti)004:1942: sh+aakya'i bstan la rnam dag tshul khrims kyi //
NK039(ti)004:1943: 'byung gnas dge slong dge 'dun 'dus pa'i sder //
NK039(ti)004:1944: bde gshegs bstan pa phyogs bcur rgyas pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1945: lhag par gsang chen rdo rje theg pa yi //
NK039(ti)004:1946: bstan pa'i snying po rgyud sde chen po drug /
NK039(ti)004:1947: de las dpal ldan rgyud rgyal 'jig rten gyi //
NK039(ti)004:1948: rin chen gcig pu gsang ba snying po yi //
NK039(ti)004:1949: rig 'dzin dge 'dun rmad byung 'dus pa'i chus //
NK039(ti)004:1950: rim gnyis lhur len bar chad med pa yis //
NK039(ti)004:1951: mthun pa'i bka' thub dge ba rgyas pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1952: khrims bzang nyams med 'phel bar mdzad du gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1953: ri sul shin tu rnal 'byor sgom pa'i sde //
NK039(ti)004:1954: g.yo med bsam gtan grub pas mdzes pa dang //
NK039(ti)004:1955: nags su zhi ba nges par 'byung ba'i sdes //
NK039(ti)004:1956: 'dod chung chog shes sbyangs brtson dpal gyis dul //
NK039(ti)004:1957: gtsug lag khang rnams lung dang rigs pa la //
NK039(ti)004:1958: kha ton klog pas rtag tu rgyas pa yis //
NK039(ti)004:1959: ngur smrig rgyal mtshan thogs pa'i rgyal ba'i 'khor //
NK039(ti)004:1960: dge 'dun bslab sde 'phel bar mdzad du gsol //
NK039(ti)004:1961: zhes rol mor bcas te gzhung nas dur khrod /
NK039(ti)004:1963: gtsang sa sgrub khang steng du rdo rje shugs kyi rgyas bzhag /
NK039(ti)004:1965: ma h+aa k+aa li sh+ri re ma ti sa p+aa ri wa ra badz+ra ar+g+ham nas /
NK039(ti)004:1967: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK039(ti)004:1968: ma ha rak+ta kha h+ais sman raka bran /
NK039(ti)004:1969: ma b+h+yohdza las byung ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK039(ti)004:1970: ce spyang bong drel 'byung ba bzhi la chib //
NK039(ti)004:1971: dpal ldan lha mo re ti mched bzhi sogs //
NK039(ti)004:1972: 'khor bcas ma mo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)004:1974: ma rnyes yongs su sogs dang yi ge brgya pa
NK039(ti)004:1975: lan gsum gyis bshags tshar nas ye shes pa gshegs
NK039(ti)004:1976: mi dgos gsungs / 'khor rnams skem ma dang bcas pa ma mo'i thugs kar bsdu /
NK039(ti)004:1977: bong bu ma mo la thim /
NK039(ti)004:1978: ma mo bdag gi thugs kar thim /
NK039(ti)004:1979: gzhal yas khang dang me rlung mi dmigs par gyur pa'i ngang mnyam par bzhag go //
NK039(ti)004:1981: kun bzang shaka thub lag na rdo rje can //
NK039(ti)004:1982: d+ha na sang kri slob dpon pad ma sogs //
NK039(ti)004:1983: dran pas srid zhi'i gdung sel yid bzhin nor //
NK039(ti)004:1984: rab 'byams rtsa rgyud bla ma'i bkra shis shog /
NK039(ti)004:1985: mchog thun dngos grub dpal 'bar he ru kah bdud dpung bye ba'i mun nag gtos chen po //
NK039(ti)004:1986: rnam par 'thags mdzad bcom ldan yi dam lha //
NK039(ti)004:1987: zhi khro dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i bkra shis shog /
NK039(ti)004:1988: dpal ldan dgyes mdzad bde chen sher phyin mo //
NK039(ti)004:1989: chos nyid rnam dag ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK039(ti)004:1990: skye med don gyi ma chen skur ston pa //
NK039(ti)004:1991: yum gyur rdo rje mkha' 'agro'ibakra shis shog /
NK039(ti)004:1992: g.yar dam dbang gis bder gshegs bstan pa srungs //
NK039(ti)004:1993: thugs rje'i dbang gis mthu chen khros par bston //
NK039(ti)004:1994: dam tshig dbang gis sgrub pa po yi mgon //
NK039(ti)004:1995: brgyud gsum dregs pa'i tshogs kyi bkra shis shog /
NK039(ti)004:1996: ces me tog char du snyil bas dge legs su bya'o //
NK039(ti)004:1997: de ltar thub bstan rin po che kho na bsam
NK039(ti)004:1998: pa'i sgrub po dam ldan rang 'dod kyis phyir chos
NK039(ti)004:1999: skyongs bsnyen pa ma yin par /
NK039(ti)004:2000: bsam pa bzang pos chos thams cad byang chub sems
NK039(ti)004:2001: kyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs pa'i lta ba la bsgom
NK039(ti)004:2002: pas snang srid ma mo'i srog nas drangs te /
NK039(ti)004:2003: phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i rol pa ci bsgrub kyang
NK039(ti)004:2004: bslu ba med pa rdo rje'i gsung gi tshad ma
NK039(ti)004:2005: yin pas / bsnyen pa rtags mtshan dus kyis drangs pa dang /
NK039(ti)004:2006: bsgrub pa las sbyor gyi gnad khel ba'i lag len
NK039(ti)004:2007: man ngag gi yi ge bzhin du khong du chud
NK039(ti)004:2008: pas / sems can gyi don du rnam pa thams
NK039(ti)004:2009: cad mkhyen pa bsgrub pa'i lam gyi bar chad sel
NK039(ti)004:2010: ba'i dgongs pa khyad par ba la /
NK039(ti)004:2011: thar 'dod dag gis sems gzhol bar bya ba ni
NK039(ti)004:2012: ched du bya ba'i don 'bras yin no zhes 'dom
NK039(ti)004:2013: mo // grub mchog du mas bsten pa'i bka' srung 'dis /
NK039(ti)004:2014: mchod chog legs par bris pa'i dge ba des //
NK039(ti)004:2015: mtha' yas 'gro kun byang chub sgrub pa la //
NK039(ti)004:2016: bar chad gdug pa mtha' dag gzhom gyur cig /
NK039(ti)004:2017: ces pa'ang bla med ma mo'i rgyud dang rgya gzhung
NK039(ti)004:2018: rnams dang 'jam pa'i dbyangs 7shar kahthoga pa chen po'i
NK039(ti)004:2019: snyan brgyud man ngag gi gzhung bzang rnams las ji
NK039(ti)004:2020: ltar 'byung ba bzhin du 'gal ba med pa'i yi
NK039(ti)004:2021: ge 'di lta bu byed du rung ba'i ltas dang
NK039(ti)004:2022: mtshan ma bzang po'ang mthong zhing nye bar gnas pa'i
NK039(ti)004:2023: dge slong blo bzang chos dbyings kyis nan du bskul
NK039(ti)004:2024: ngor / sh+aakya'i dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa si
NK039(ti)004:2025: tu pa chos kyi rgya mtsho'i sprin gyis bkod pa
NK039(ti)004:2026: gsang chen rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud sde'i bstan pa
NK039(ti)004:2027: rin po che 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu 'phel
